"autoformat.xhp\n"
"par_id3149401\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the AutoFormat feature to quickly apply a format to a selected cell range."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຄຸນສົມບັດ AutoFormat ເພື່ອນຳໃຊ້ຮູບແບບກັບຊ່ວງຫ້ອງທີ່ເລືອກໄດ້ຢ່າງວ່ອງໄວ."

