msgstr "ກົດ <emph>OK</emph> ເພື່ອນຳໃຊ້ຮູບແບບ AutoFormat ແລະ ປິດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ."

#. EAyCv
#: autoformat.xhp
msgctxt ""
"autoformat.xhp\n"
"par_id3149210\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In case the color of the cell contents does not change, make sure <menuitem>View - Value Highlighting</menuitem> is disabled."
msgstr "ໃນກໍລະນີທີ່ສີຂອງເນື້ອໃນຫ້ອງບໍ່ປ່ຽນແປງ, ໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າ <menuitem>View - Value Highlighting</menuitem> ຖືກປິດການໃຊ້ງານແລ້ວ."

