msgstr "ການຄິດໄລ່ລຳດັບ (Series) ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ"

#. jCpXS
#: calc_series.xhp
msgctxt ""
"calc_series.xhp\n"
"bm_id3150769\n"
