#. eesNk
#: calculate.xhp
msgctxt ""
"calculate.xhp\n"
"par_id3147343\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The result of the formula appears in the cell. If you want, you can edit the formula in the input line of the Formula bar."
msgstr "ຜົນລັບຂອງສູດຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນໃນຫ້ອງ. ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການ, ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂສູດໄດ້ໃນແຖບການປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນຂອງແຖບສູດ."

#. FgPuF
#: calculate.xhp
msgctxt ""
"calculate.xhp\n"
"par_id3155378\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you edit a formula, the new result is calculated automatically."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານແກ້ໄຂສູດ, ຜົນລັບໃໝ່ຈະຖືກຄິດໄລ່ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. btgfD
