"par_id3150751\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Result"
msgstr "ຜົນລັບ"

#. 6fWoa
#: cellcopy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cellcopy.xhp\n"
"par_id3149018\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Cells were filtered by AutoFilters, standard filters or advanced filters."
msgstr "ຫ້ອງຖືກຕອງໂດຍ AutoFilters, ຕົວຕອງມາດຕະຖານ ຫຼື ຕົວຕອງຂັ້ນສູງ."

#. M4Edv
#: cellcopy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cellcopy.xhp\n"
"par_id3150044\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Copy, delete, move, or format a selection of currently visible cells."
msgstr "ສຳເນົາ, ລຶບ, ຍ້າຍ ຫຼື ຈັດຮູບແບບການເລືອກຂອງຫ້ອງທີ່ເບິ່ງເຫັນໄດ້ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. fV6ro
#: cellcopy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cellcopy.xhp\n"
"par_id3146918\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Only the visible cells of the selection are copied, deleted, moved, or formatted."
msgstr "ສະເພາະຫ້ອງທີ່ເຫັນໄດ້ຂອງການເລືອກເທົ່ານັ້ນທີ່ຈະຖືກສຳເນົາ, ລຶບ, ຍ້າຍ ຫຼື ຈັດຮູບແບບ."

#. E9sMe
#: cellcopy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cellcopy.xhp\n"
"par_id3166427\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Cells were hidden using the <emph>Hide</emph> command in the context menu of the row or column headers, or through an <link href=\"text/scalc/01/12080000.xhp\">outline</link>."
msgstr "ຫ້ອງຖືກເຊື່ອງໄວ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ <emph>Hide</emph> ໃນເມນູຄລິກຂວາຂອງຫົວແຖວ ຫຼື ຫົວຖັນ, ຫຼື ຜ່ານ <link href=\"text/scalc/01/12080000.xhp\">outline</link>."

#. hCVpN
#: cellcopy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cellcopy.xhp\n"
"par_id3152990\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Copy, delete, move, or format a selection of currently visible cells."
msgstr "ສຳເນົາ, ລຶບ, ຍ້າຍ ຫຼື ຈັດຮູບແບບການເລືອກຂອງຫ້ອງທີ່ເບິ່ງເຫັນໄດ້ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. VccAs
#: cellcopy.xhp
msgctxt ""
"cellcopy.xhp\n"
"par_id3154371\n"
"help.text"
msgid "By default, all cells of the selection, including the hidden cells, are copied, deleted, moved, or formatted. Restrict the selection to visible rows choosing <menuitem>Edit - Select - Select Visible Rows Only</menuitem> or to visible columns choosing <menuitem>Edit - Select - Select Visible Columns Only</menuitem>."
msgstr "ໂດຍຄ່າມາດຕະຖານ, ທຸກຫ້ອງຂອງການເລືອກ ລວມທັງຫ້ອງທີ່ຖືກເຊື່ອງໄວ້ ຈະຖືກສຳເນົາ, ລຶບ, ຍ້າຍ ຫຼື ຈັດຮູບແບບ. ໃຫ້ຈຳກັດການເລືອກສະເພາະແຖວທີ່ເຫັນໄດ້ໂດຍເລືອກ <menuitem>Edit - Select - Select Visible Rows Only</menuitem> ຫຼື ສະເພາະຖັນທີ່ເຫັນໄດ້ໂດຍເລືອກ <menuitem>Edit - Select - Select Visible Columns Only</menuitem>."

#. rBtUY
