msgstr "<variable id=\"csv_formula\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/csv_formula.xhp\">ການນຳເຂົ້າ ແລະ ການສົ່ງອອກໄຟລ໌ຂໍ້ຄວາມ CSV ທີ່ມີສູດ</link></variable>"

#. 7kmDr
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3149402\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Comma separated values (CSV) files are text files that contain the cell contents of a single sheet. Commas, semicolons, or other characters can be used as the field delimiters between the cells. Text strings are put in quotation marks, numbers are written without quotation marks."
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ Comma separated values (CSV) ແມ່ນໄຟລ໌ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ມີເນື້ອໃນຂອງເຊວຂອງແຜ່ນງານດຽວ. ສາມາດໃຊ້ຈຸດ, ຈ້ຳຈຸດ ຫຼື ຕົວອັກສອນອື່ນໆເປັນຕົວຂັ້ນລະຫວ່າງເຊວໄດ້. ຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະຖືກໃສ່ໄວ້ໃນເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳເວົ້າ, ສ່ວນຕົວເລກຈະຖືກຂຽນໂດຍບໍ່ມີເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳເວົ້າ."

#. 5E4aN
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150715\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To Import a CSV File"
msgstr "ວິທີການນຳເຂົ້າໄຟລ໌ CSV"

#. iNsCc
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3153709\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>File - Open</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ເປີດ</emph>."

#. iPsQg
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3155445\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>File type</emph> field, select the format \"Text CSV\". Select the file and click <emph>Open</emph>. When a file has the .csv extension, the file type is automatically recognized."
msgstr "ໃນຟິວ <emph>ປະເພດໄຟລ໌</emph>, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຮູບແບບ \"Text CSV\". ເລືອກໄຟລ໌ແລ້ວຄລິກ <emph>ເປີດ</emph>. ເມື່ອໄຟລ໌ມີນາມສະກຸນ .csv, ປະເພດໄຟລ໌ຈະຖືກຮັບຮູ້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. U4nRf
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3149565\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You will see the <item type=\"menuitem\">Text Import</item> dialog. Click <item type=\"menuitem\">OK</item>."
msgstr "ທ່ານຈະເຫັນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <item type=\"menuitem\">ການນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ຄວາມ</item>. ຄລິກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ຕົກລົງ</item>."

#. adhCg
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3149255\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the csv file contains formulas, but you want to import the results of those formulas, then choose <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - View</emph> and clear the <emph>Formulas</emph> check box."
msgstr "ຖ້າໄຟລ໌ csv ມີສູດ, ແຕ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການນຳເຂົ້າຜົນໄດ້ຮັບຂອງສູດເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ສິ່ງທີ່ມັກ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - ມຸມມອງ</emph> ແລະ ຍົກເລີກການໝາຍເອົາຫ້ອງ <emph>ສູດ</emph>."

#. JTAdg
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154022\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To Export Formulas and Values as CSV Files"
msgstr "ວິທີການສົ່ງອອກສູດ ແລະ ຄ່າເປັນໄຟລ໌ CSV"

#. fWwZt
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3150342\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the sheet to be written as a csv file."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ແຜ່ນງານທີ່ຈະຂຽນເປັນໄຟລ໌ csv."

#. nJJjE
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3166423\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you want to export the formulas as formulas, for example, in the form =SUM(A1:B5), proceed as follows:"
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການສົ່ງອອກສູດໃຫ້ຢູ່ໃນຮູບແບບສູດ, ຕົວຢ່າງໃນຮູບແບບ =SUM(A1:B5), ໃຫ້ດຳເນີນການດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. S9LAC
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3155111\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - View</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ສິ່ງທີ່ມັກ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - ມຸມມອງ</emph>."

#. 4oXKB
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3150200\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Under <emph>Display</emph>, mark the <emph>Formulas</emph> check box. Click <emph>OK</emph>."
msgstr "ພາຍໃຕ້ <emph>ການສະແດງຜົນ</emph>, ໃຫ້ໝາຍເອົາຫ້ອງ <emph>ສູດ</emph>. ຄລິກ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>."

#. iwN9i
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3154484\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you want to export the calculation results instead of the formulas, do not mark <emph>Formulas</emph>."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການສົ່ງອອກຜົນການຄຳນວນແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນສູດ, ບໍ່ຕ້ອງໝາຍເອົາຫ້ອງ <emph>ສູດ</emph>."

#. a5ChK
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3148702\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>File - Save as</emph>. You will see the <emph>Save as</emph> dialog."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ໄຟລ໌ - ບັນທຶກເປັນ</emph>. ທ່ານຈະເຫັນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ບັນທຶກເປັນ</emph>."

#. wc7Fy
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3153912\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the               <item type=\"menuitem\">File type</item> field select the format \"Text CSV\"."
msgstr "ໃນຟິວ <item type=\"menuitem\">ປະເພດໄຟລ໌</item>, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຮູບແບບ \"Text CSV\"."

#. jFEFh
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3157978\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter a name and click <emph>Save</emph>."
msgstr "ປ້ອນຊື່ແລ້ວຄລິກ <emph>ບັນທຶກ</emph>."

#. Z69Sc
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3152869\n"
"help.text"
msgid "From the <emph>Export of text files</emph> dialog that appears, select the character set and the field and text delimiters for the data to be exported, and confirm with <emph>OK</emph>."
msgstr "ຈາກກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ການສົ່ງອອກໄຟລ໌ຂໍ້ຄວາມ</emph> ທີ່ປາກົດຂຶ້ນ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຊຸດຕົວອັກສອນ ແລະ ຕົວຂັ້ນຟິວ ແລະ ຂໍ້ຄວາມສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຈະສົ່ງອອກ, ແລ້ວຍືນຍັນດ້ວຍປຸ່ມ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>."

#. yPP3a
#: csv_formula.xhp
msgctxt ""
"csv_formula.xhp\n"
"par_id3150050\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If necessary, after you have saved, clear the <emph>Formulas</emph> check box to see the calculated results in the table again."
msgstr "ຖ້າຈຳເປັນ, ຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ທ່ານບັນທຶກແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ຍົກເລີກການໝາຍເອົາຫ້ອງ <emph>ສູດ</emph> ເພື່ອເບິ່ງຜົນການຄຳນວນໃນຕາຕະລາງອີກຄັ້ງ."

