"formula_value.xhp\n"
"par_id3150010\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you want to display the formulas in the cells, for example in the form =SUM(A1:B5), proceed as follows:"
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການສະແດງສູດໃນຫ້ອງຕາຕະລາງ, ຕົວຢ່າງໃນຮູບແບບ =SUM(A1:B5), ໃຫ້ປະຕິບັດດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. PADBf
#: formula_value.xhp
msgctxt ""
"formula_value.xhp\n"
"par_id3151116\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - View</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - ມຸມມອງ</emph>."

#. 6tdYB
