#. Q5PPt
#: formula_value.xhp
msgctxt ""
"formula_value.xhp\n"
"par_id3147396\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you want to view the calculation results instead of the formula, do not mark the Formulas box."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການເບິ່ງຜົນການຄິດໄລ່ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນສູດ, ບໍ່ຕ້ອງໝາຍຕິກເອົາຊ່ອງ ສູດ."

