msgstr "ໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ຊອກຫາ</emph>, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນ <item type=\"input\">^[0-9]</item>"

#. 6gHkJ
#: integer_leading_zero.xhp
msgctxt ""
"integer_leading_zero.xhp\n"
"par_id3155068\n"
