#. DoYMT
#: mark_cells.xhp
msgctxt ""
"mark_cells.xhp\n"
"par_id61754050643440\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To select a rectangular block of cells surrounded by empty cells, place the cursor inside the block and press <keycode>Ctrl + A</keycode>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເລືອກບລັອກຫ້ອງຕາຕະລາງຮູບສີ່ແຈສາກທີ່ອ້ອມຮອບດ້ວຍຫ້ອງຫວ່າງເປົ່າ, ໃຫ້ວາງເຄີເຊີໄວ້ໃນບລັອກນັ້ນແລ້ວກົດ <keycode>Ctrl + A</keycode>."

#. BBU2x
#: mark_cells.xhp
msgctxt ""
