#. mX8Gh
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"hd_id3145171\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Multiple Operations in Columns or Rows"
msgstr "ຫຼາຍການດຳເນີນການໃນຖັນ ຫຼື ແຖວ"

#. GgvB4
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id4123966\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <item type=\"menuitem\">Data - Multiple Operations</item> command provides a planning tool for \"what if\" questions. In your spreadsheet, you enter a formula to calculate a result from values that are stored in other cells. Then, you set up a cell range where you enter some fixed values, and the Multiple Operations command will calculate the results depending on the formula."
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງ <item type=\"menuitem\">ຂໍ້ມູນ - ຫຼາຍການດຳເນີນການ</item> ໃຫ້ເຄື່ອງມືການວາງແຜນສຳລັບຄຳຖາມປະເພດ \"ຈະເກີດຫຍັງຂຶ້ນຖ້າ\". ໃນແຜ່ນວຽກຂອງທ່ານ, ທ່ານປ້ອນສູດເພື່ອຄິດໄລ່ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບຈາກຄ່າທີ່ເກັບໄວ້ໃນຫ້ອງອື່ນ. ຈາກນັ້ນ, ທ່ານກຳນົດຊ່ວງຫ້ອງຕາຕະລາງເພື່ອປ້ອນຄ່າຄົງທີ່ບາງຢ່າງ, ແລະ ຄຳສັ່ງ ຫຼາຍການດຳເນີນການ ຈະຄິດໄລ່ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບໃຫ້ຕາມສູດນັ້ນ."

#. wW4Vg
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3156424\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>Formulas</emph> field, enter the cell reference to the formula that applies to the data range. In the <emph>Column input cell/Row input cell</emph> field, enter the cell reference to the corresponding cell that is part of the formula. This can be explained best by examples:"
msgstr "ໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ສູດ</emph>, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນການອ້າງອີງຫ້ອງຕາຕະລາງໄປຫາສູດທີ່ໃຊ້ກັບຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ. ໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ຫ້ອງຕາຕະລາງປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນຖັນ/ຫ້ອງຕາຕະລາງປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນແຖວ</emph>, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນການອ້າງອີງໄປຫາຫ້ອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງເຊິ່ງເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງສູດ. ສາມາດອະທິບາຍໄດ້ດີທີ່ສຸດຜ່ານຕົວຢ່າງ:"

#. aZap6
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"hd_id3159153\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ"

#. 7GHff
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3153189\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You produce toys which you sell for $10 each. Each toy costs $2 to make, in addition to which you have fixed costs of $10,000 per year. How much profit will you make in a year if you sell a particular number of toys?"
msgstr "ທ່ານຜະລິດເຄື່ອງຫຼິ້ນເຊິ່ງຂາຍໃນລາຄາ $10 ຕໍ່ຊິ້ນ. ເຄື່ອງຫຼິ້ນແຕ່ລະຊິ້ນມີຕົ້ນທຶນການຜະລິດ $2, ນອກຈາກນັ້ນທ່ານຍັງມີຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍຄົງທີ່ $10,000 ຕໍ່ປີ. ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ກຳໄລເທົ່າໃດໃນໜຶ່ງປີ ຫາກທ່ານຂາຍເຄື່ອງຫຼິ້ນໄດ້ຕາມຈຳນວນທີ່ກຳນົດ?"

#. vdeBS
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id6478774\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id1621753\" src=\"media/helpimg/what-if.png\"><alt id=\"alt_id1621753\">what-if sheet area</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id1621753\" src=\"media/helpimg/what-if.png\"><alt id=\"alt_id1621753\">ພື້ນທີ່ແຜ່ນວຽກ ຖ້າ-ວ່າ</alt></image>"

#. KavvR
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"hd_id3145239\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Calculating With One Formula and One Variable"
msgstr "ການຄິດໄລ່ດ້ວຍໜຶ່ງສູດ ແລະ ໜຶ່ງຕົວປ່ຽນ"

#. nCki4
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3146888\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To calculate the profit, first enter any number as the quantity (items sold) - in this example 2000. The profit is found from the formula Profit=Quantity * (Selling price - Direct costs) - Fixed costs. Enter this formula in B5."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຄິດໄລ່ກຳໄລ, ທຳອິດໃຫ້ປ້ອນຕົວເລກໃດໜຶ່ງເປັນຈຳນວນ (ຊິ້ນທີ່ຂາຍໄດ້) - ໃນຕົວຢ່າງນີ້ແມ່ນ 2000. ກຳໄລຈະຖືກຄິດໄລ່ຈາກສູດ ກຳໄລ = ຈຳນວນ * (ລາຄາຂາຍ - ຕົ້ນທຶນໂດຍກົງ) - ຄ່າໃຊ້ຈ່າຍຄົງທີ່. ປ້ອນສູດນີ້ໃນ B5."

#. 4zUKz
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3157875\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In column D enter given annual sales, one below the other; for example, 500 to 5000, in steps of 500."
msgstr "ໃນຖັນ D ໃຫ້ປ້ອນຍອດຂາຍລາຍປີທີ່ກຳນົດໃຫ້, ລຽງລົງມາຕາມລຳດັບ; ຕົວຢ່າງ: 500 ຫາ 5000, ໂດຍເພີ່ມຂຶ້ນເທື່ອລະ 500."

#. vABD4
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3159115\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the range D2:E11, and thus the values in column D and the empty cells alongside in column E."
msgstr "ເລືອກຊ່ວງ D2:E11, ເຊິ່ງລວມມີຄ່າໃນຖັນ D ແລະ ຫ້ອງຫວ່າງເປົ່າທາງຂ້າງໃນຖັນ E."

#. b4zBY
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3149723\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Data - Multiple operations</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ຂໍ້ມູນ - ຫຼາຍການດຳເນີນການ</emph>."

#. p8VjP
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3149149\n"
"help.text"
msgid "With the cursor in the <emph>Formulas </emph>field, click cell B5."
msgstr "ວາງເຄີເຊີໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ສູດ</emph>, ແລ້ວຄລິກຫ້ອງ B5."

#. NBWeD
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3149355\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Set the cursor in the <emph>Column input cell</emph> field and click cell B4. This means that B4, the quantity, is the variable in the formula, which is replaced by the selected column values."
msgstr "ວາງເຄີເຊີໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ຫ້ອງຕາຕະລາງປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນຖັນ</emph> ແລ້ວຄລິກຫ້ອງ B4. ນີ້ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າ B4 ຫຼື ຈຳນວນ, ແມ່ນຕົວປ່ຽນໃນສູດ ເຊິ່ງຈະຖືກປ່ຽນແທນດ້ວຍຄ່າໃນຖັນທີ່ເລືອກ."

#. SyPmA
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3149009\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Close the dialog with <emph>OK</emph>. You see the profits for the different quantities in column E."
msgstr "ປິດປ່ອງຢ້ຽມດ້ວຍການຄລິກ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>. ທ່ານຈະເຫັນກຳໄລສຳລັບຈຳນວນທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນໃນຖັນ E."

#. CqtUM
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"hd_id3148725\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Calculating with Several Formulas Simultaneously"
msgstr "ການຄິດໄລ່ດ້ວຍຫຼາຍສູດພ້ອມກັນ"

#. DxqGZ
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3146880\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Delete column E."
msgstr "ລົບຖັນ E."

#. h4umZ
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3154675\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter the following formula in C5: = B5 / B4. You are now calculating the annual profit per item sold."
msgstr "ປ້ອນສູດຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ໃນ C5: = B5 / B4. ຕອນນີ້ທ່ານກຳລັງຄິດໄລ່ກຳໄລປະຈຳປີຕໍ່ລາຍການທີ່ຂາຍອອກ."

#. GpoD9
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3148885\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the range D2:F11, thus three columns."
msgstr "ເລືອກຂອບເຂດ D2:F11, ເຊິ່ງລວມມີສາມຖັນ."

#. 5GyFY
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3147474\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Data - Multiple Operations</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ຂໍ້ມູນ - ການດຳເນີນການຫຼາຍຢ່າງ</emph>."

#. vVE2F
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3154846\n"
"help.text"
msgid "With the cursor in the <emph>Formulas</emph> field, select cells B5 thru C5."
msgstr "ວາງເຄີເຊີໃນຫ້ອງ <emph>ສູດ</emph>, ແລ້ວເລືອກຫ້ອງ B5 ຫາ C5."

#. CBN2h
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3153931\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Set the cursor in the <emph>Column input cell</emph> field and click cell B4."
msgstr "ວາງເຄີເຊີໃນຫ້ອງ <emph>ຫ້ອງປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນຖັນ</emph> ແລ້ວຄລິກທີ່ຫ້ອງ B4."

#. mfN9d
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3150862\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Close the dialog with <emph>OK</emph>. You will now see the profits in column E and the annual profit per item in column F."
msgstr "ປິດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບດ້ວຍ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>. ຕອນນີ້ທ່ານຈະເຫັນກຳໄລໃນຖັນ E ແລະ ກຳໄລປະຈຳປີຕໍ່ລາຍການໃນຖັນ F."

#. avEUy
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"hd_id3146139\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Multiple Operations Across Rows and Columns"
msgstr "ການດຳເນີນການຫຼາຍຢ່າງຜ່ານແຖວ ແລະ ຖັນ"

#. 3abTJ
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3148584\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> allows you to carry out joint multiple operations for columns and rows in so-called cross-tables. The formula cell has to refer to both the data range arranged in rows and the one arranged in columns. Select the range defined by both data ranges and call the multiple operation dialog. Enter the reference to the formula in the <emph>Formulas</emph> field. The <emph>Row input cell</emph> and the <emph>Column input cell</emph> fields are used to enter the reference to the corresponding cells of the formula."
msgstr "<item type=\"productname\">%PRODUCTNAME</item> ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ທ່ານດຳເນີນການຫຼາຍຢ່າງຮ່ວມກັນສຳລັບຖັນ ແລະ ແຖວໃນຕາຕະລາງແບບໄຂວ່. ຫ້ອງສູດຕ້ອງອ້າງອີງເຖິງທັງຂອບເຂດຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຈັດລຽງເປັນແຖວ ແລະ ຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຈັດລຽງເປັນຖັນ. ເລືອກຂອບເຂດທີ່ກຳນົດໂດຍຂອບເຂດຂໍ້ມູນທັງສອງ ແລ້ວເອີ້ນໃຊ້ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບການດຳເນີນການຫຼາຍຢ່າງ. ປ້ອນການອ້າງອີງເຖິງສູດໃນຫ້ອງ <emph>ສູດ</emph>. ຫ້ອງ <emph>ຫ້ອງປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນແຖວ</emph> ແລະ <emph>ຫ້ອງປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນຖັນ</emph> ແມ່ນໃຊ້ເພື່ອປ້ອນການອ້າງອີງເຖິງຫ້ອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງຂອງສູດ."

#. uHGGD
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149949\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Calculating with Two Variables"
msgstr "ການຄິດໄລ່ດ້ວຍສອງຕົວປ່ຽນ"

#. 7MGG4
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3154808\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Consider columns A and B of the sample table above. You now want to vary not just the quantity produced annually, but also the selling price, and you are interested in the profit in each case."
msgstr "ພິຈາລະນາຖັນ A ແລະ B ຂອງຕາຕະລາງຕົວຢ່າງຂ້າງເທິງ. ຕອນນີ້ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປ່ຽນແປງບໍ່ພຽງແຕ່ປະລິມານການຜະລິດປະຈຳປີເທົ່ານັ້ນ, ແຕ່ຍັງລວມເຖິງລາຄາຂາຍ, ແລະ ທ່ານສົນໃຈກຳໄລໃນແຕ່ລະກໍລະນີ."

#. kRNub
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3149731\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Expand the table shown above. D2 thru D11 contain the numbers 500, 1000 and so on, up to 5000. In E1 through H1 enter the numbers 8, 10, 15 and 20."
msgstr "ຂະຫຍາຍຕາຕະລາງທີ່ສະແດງຂ້າງເທິງ. D2 ຫາ D11 ບັນຈຸຕົວເລກ 500, 1000 ແລະ ຕໍ່ໆໄປ ຈົນເຖິງ 5000. ໃນ E1 ຫາ H1 ໃຫ້ປ້ອນຕົວເລກ 8, 10, 15 ແລະ 20."

#. LdMQc
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3152810\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the range D1:H11."
msgstr "ເລືອກຂອບເຂດ D1:H11."

#. FKGVk
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3153620\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Data - Multiple Operations</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ຂໍ້ມູນ - ການດຳເນີນການຫຼາຍຢ່າງ</emph>."

#. uv9gg
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3149981\n"
"help.text"
msgid "With the cursor in the <emph>Formulas</emph> field, click cell B5."
msgstr "ວາງເຄີເຊີໃນຫ້ອງ <emph>ສູດ</emph> ແລ້ວຄລິກທີ່ຫ້ອງ B5."

#. ABmDF
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3156113\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Set the cursor in the <emph>Row input cell</emph> field and click cell B1. This means that B1, the selling price, is the horizontally entered variable (with the values 8, 10, 15 and 20)."
msgstr "ວາງເຄີເຊີໃນຫ້ອງ <emph>ຫ້ອງປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນແຖວ</emph> ແລ້ວຄລິກທີ່ຫ້ອງ B1. ນີ້ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າ B1, ລາຄາຂາຍ, ແມ່ນຕົວປ່ຽນທີ່ປ້ອນເຂົ້າໃນລັກສະນະແນວນອນ (ດ້ວຍຄ່າ 8, 10, 15 ແລະ 20)."

#. yrzWJ
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3154049\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Set the cursor in the <emph>Column input cell</emph> field and click in B4. This means that B4, the quantity, is the vertically entered variable."
msgstr "ວາງເຄີເຊີໃນຫ້ອງ <emph>ຫ້ອງປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນຖັນ</emph> ແລ້ວຄລິກໃນ B4. ນີ້ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າ B4, ປະລິມານ, ແມ່ນຕົວປ່ຽນທີ່ປ້ອນເຂົ້າໃນລັກສະນະແນວຕັ້ງ."

#. YEQAH
#: multioperation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"multioperation.xhp\n"
"par_id3149141\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Close the dialog with OK. You see the profits for the different selling prices in the range E2:H11."
msgstr "ປິດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບດ້ວຍ ຕົກລົງ. ທ່ານຈະເຫັນກຳໄລສຳລັບລາຄາຂາຍທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນໃນຂອບເຂດ E2:H11."

#. fgJoa
