"bm_id14648\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>exporting;cells</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>printing; cells</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ranges;print ranges</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>PDF export of print ranges</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>cell ranges; printing</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>cells; print ranges</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>print ranges</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>clearing, see also deleting/removing</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>defining;print ranges</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>extending print ranges</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>deleting;print ranges</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ການສົ່ງອອກ; ຫ້ອງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການພິມ; ຫ້ອງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຂອບເຂດ; ຂອບເຂດການພິມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການສົ່ງອອກ PDF ຂອງຂອບເຂດການພິມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຂອບເຂດຫ້ອງ; ການພິມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຫ້ອງ; ຂອບເຂດການພິມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຂອບເຂດການພິມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການລຶບລ້າງ, ເບິ່ງເພີ່ມເຕີມ ການລຶບ/ການເອົາອອກ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການກຳນົດ; ຂອບເຂດການພິມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການຂະຫຍາຍຂອບເຂດການພິມ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການລຶບ; ຂອບເຂດການພິມ</bookmark_value>"

#. USFyE
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN108D7\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"printranges\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/printranges.xhp\">Defining Print Ranges on a Sheet</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"printranges\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/printranges.xhp\">ການກຳນົດຂອບເຂດການພິມໃນແຜ່ນງານ</link></variable>"

#. h4dAF
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN108F5\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can define which range of cells on a spreadsheet to print."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດຂອບເຂດຂອງຫ້ອງໃນສະເປຣດຊີດທີ່ຈະພິມໄດ້."

#. sD9qE
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN108FB\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The cells on the sheet that are not part of the defined print range are not printed or exported. Sheets without a defined print range are not printed and not exported to a PDF file, unless the document uses the Excel file format."
msgstr "ຫ້ອງໃນແຜ່ນງານທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງຂອບເຂດການພິມທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ຈະບໍ່ຖືກພິມ ຫຼື ສົ່ງອອກ. ແຜ່ນງານທີ່ບໍ່ມີການກຳນົດຂອບເຂດການພິມຈະບໍ່ຖືກພິມ ແລະ ບໍ່ຖືກສົ່ງອອກເປັນໄຟລ໌ PDF, ຍົກເວັ້ນເອກະສານນັ້ນໃຊ້ຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ Excel."

#. HkA7y
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN1077A\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For files opened in Excel format, all sheets that do not contain a defined print range are printed. The same behavior occurs when you export the Excel formatted spreadsheet to a PDF file."
msgstr "ສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເປີດໃນຮູບແບບ Excel, ທຸກແຜ່ນງານທີ່ບໍ່ມີຂອບເຂດການພິມທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ຈະຖືກພິມອອກມາ. ພຶດຕິກໍາດຽວກັນນີ້ຈະເກີດຂຶ້ນເມື່ອທ່ານສົ່ງອອກສະເປຣດຊີດໃນຮູບແບບ Excel ເປັນໄຟລ໌ PDF."

#. 62UF5
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN108FE\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To Define a Print Range"
msgstr "ເພື່ອທຳການກຳນົດຂອບເຂດການພິມ"

#. tffSG
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN10905\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the cells that you want to print."
msgstr "ເລືອກຫ້ອງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການພິມ."

#. qPKQF
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN10909\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Format - Print Ranges - Define</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ຮູບແບບ - ຂອບເຂດການພິມ - ກຳນົດ</emph>."

#. 5GFUH
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN10910\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To Add Cells to a Print Range"
msgstr "ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຫ້ອງເຂົ້າໃນຂອບເຂດການພິມ"

#. fwkxc
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN10917\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the cells that you want to add to the existing print range."
msgstr "ເລືອກຫ້ອງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນຂອບເຂດການພິມທີ່ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວ."

#. uNLYf
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN1091B\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Format - Print Ranges - Add</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ຮູບແບບ - ຂອບເຂດການພິມ - ເພີ່ມ</emph>."

#. Xj8rT
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN10922\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To Clear a Print Range"
msgstr "ເພື່ອທຳການລຶບລ້າງຂອບເຂດການພິມ"

#. dYHcz
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN10929\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Format - Print Ranges - Clear</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ຮູບແບບ - ຂອບເຂດການພິມ - ລຶບລ້າງ</emph>."

#. GLmBw
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN10953\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Using the Page Break Preview to Edit Print Ranges"
msgstr "ການໃຊ້ຕົວຢ່າງແບ່ງໜ້າເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂຂອບເຂດການພິມ"

#. fA865
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN1093E\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>Page Break Preview</emph>, print ranges as well as page break regions are outlined by a blue border and contain a centered page number in gray. Nonprinting areas have a gray background."
msgstr "ໃນ <emph>ຕົວຢ່າງແບ່ງໜ້າ</emph>, ຂອບເຂດການພິມ ລວມທັງພື້ນທີ່ແບ່ງໜ້າຈະຖືກລ້ອມຮອບດ້ວຍຂອບສີຟ້າ ແລະ ມີເລກໜ້າສີເທົາຢູ່ເຄິ່ງກາງ. ພື້ນທີ່ທີ່ບໍ່ມີການພິມຈະມີພື້ນຫຼັງເປັນສີເທົາ."

#. S5enN
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_id3153143\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To define a new page break region, drag the border to a new location. When you define a new page break region, an automatic page break is replaced by a manual page break."
msgstr "ເພື່ອທຳການກຳນົດພື້ນທີ່ແບ່ງໜ້າໃໝ່, ໃຫ້ລາກຂອບໄປທີ່ຕຳແໜ່ງໃໝ່. ເມື່ອທ່ານກຳນົດພື້ນທີ່ແບ່ງໜ້າໃໝ່, ຕົວແບ່ງໜ້າອັດຕະໂນມັດຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ດ້ວຍຕົວແບ່ງໜ້າດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ."

#. DCNh4
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN10930\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To View and Edit Print Ranges"
msgstr "ເພື່ອທຳການເບິ່ງ ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂຂອບເຂດການພິມ"

#. KmLhz
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN10937\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>View - Page Break Preview</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ການເບິ່ງ - ຕົວຢ່າງແບ່ງໜ້າ</emph>."

#. d3cdC
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN1082A\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To change the default zoom factor of the <emph>Page Break Preview</emph>, double click the percentage value on the <emph>Status</emph> bar, and select a new zoom factor."
msgstr "ເພື່ອປ່ຽນອັດຕາການຂະຫຍາຍເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງ <emph>ຕົວຢ່າງແບ່ງໜ້າ</emph>, ໃຫ້ດັບເບີ້ນຄລິກຄ່າເປີເຊັນໃນແຖບ <emph>ສະຖານະ</emph>, ແລ້ວເລືອກອັດຕາການຂະຫຍາຍໃໝ່."

#. RFe8B
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN10836\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Edit the print range."
msgstr "ແກ້ໄຂຂອບເຂດການພິມ."

#. dQeMn
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN10944\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To change the size of a print range, drag a border of the range to a new location."
msgstr "ເພື່ອປ່ຽນຂະໜາດຂອງຂອບເຂດການພິມ, ໃຫ້ລາກຂອບຂອງຂອບເຂດໄປທີ່ຕຳແໜ່ງໃໝ່."

#. HwnGq
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_id3151075\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To delete a manual page break that is contained in a print range, drag the border of the page break outside of the print range."
msgstr "ເພື່ອລຶບຕົວແບ່ງໜ້າດ້ວຍຕົນເອງທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນຂອບເຂດການພິມ, ໃຫ້ລາກຂອບຂອງຕົວແບ່ງໜ້າອອກໄປນອກຂອບເຂດການພິມ."

#. xLgnw
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN10948\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To clear a print range, drag a border of the range onto the opposite border of the range."
msgstr "ເພື່ອລຶບລ້າງຂອບເຂດການພິມ, ໃຫ້ລາກຂອບເບື້ອງໜຶ່ງຂອງຂອບເຂດໄປທັບກັບຂອບເບື້ອງກົງກັນຂ້າມ."

#. wATRM
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN10862\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To exit the <emph>Page Break Preview</emph>, choose <emph>View - Normal</emph>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອອອກຈາກ <emph>ຕົວຢ່າງແບ່ງໜ້າ</emph>, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <emph>ການເບິ່ງ - ປົກກະຕິ</emph>."

#. D7AdB
#: printranges.xhp
msgctxt ""
"printranges.xhp\n"
"par_idN109CF\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/05080300.xhp\">Editing Print Ranges</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/05080300.xhp\">ການແກ້ໄຂຂອບເຂດການພິມ</link>"

