#. yDjtk
#: row_height.xhp
msgctxt ""
"row_height.xhp\n"
"par_id3154020\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the area of the headers on the separator below the current row, keep the mouse button pressed and drag up or down in order to change the row height."
