#. FEwcj
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"par_id301585177069332\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Calc offers the Subtotals tool as a more comprehensive alternative to the <link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060106.xhp#Section12\">SUBTOTAL function</link>. In contrast to SUBTOTAL, which only works on a single array, the Subtotals tool can create subtotals for up to three arrays arranged in labeled columns. It also groups subtotals by category and sorts them automatically, thereby eliminating the need to apply AutoFilters and filter categories by hand."
msgstr "Calc ມີເຄື່ອງມືຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍ (Subtotals) ເປັນທາງເລືອກທີ່ຄອບຄຸມກວ່າ <link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060106.xhp#Section12\">ຟັງຊັນ SUBTOTAL</link>. ຕ່າງຈາກ SUBTOTAL ທີ່ເຮັດວຽກສະເພາະກັບອາເຣດຽວ, ເຄື່ອງມືຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍສາມາດສ້າງຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍໄດ້ສູງສຸດສາມອາເຣທີ່ຈັດລຽງໃນຖັນທີ່ມີຫົວຂໍ້. ມັນຍັງຈັດກຸ່ມຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍຕາມປະເພດ ແລະ ຈັດລຽງໃຫ້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ, ເຮັດໃຫ້ບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງໃຊ້ AutoFilters ແລະ ຕອງປະເພດດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ."

#. NEkbi
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"hd_id891585177511329\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Using the Subtotals tool"
msgstr "ການໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງມືຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍ"

#. kwLkR
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"par_id91585177517697\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To insert subtotal values into a worksheet:"
msgstr "ເພື່ອແຊກຄ່າຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍລົງໃນແຜ່ນງານ:"

#. DKZ3o
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"par_id241585177550504\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the cell range for the subtotals that you want to calculate, and remember to include the column heading labels. Alternatively, click on a single cell within your data to allow Calc to automatically identify the range."
msgstr "ເລືອກຊ່ວງເຊວສຳລັບຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການຄຳນວນ, ຢ່າລືມລວມເອົາຫົວຖັນນຳ. ຫຼືອີກວິທີໜຶ່ງ, ຄລິກໃສ່ເຊວໃດໜຶ່ງພາຍໃນຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານເພື່ອໃຫ້ Calc ກຳນົດຊ່ວງໃຫ້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. QiBqE
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"par_id421585177574387\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <menuitem>Data - Subtotals</menuitem> to open the Subtotals dialog."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <menuitem>ຂໍ້ມູນ - ຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍ</menuitem> ເພື່ອເປີດປ່ອງຢ້ຽມຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍ."

#. BwAst
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"par_id41585177608508\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>Group by</emph> drop-down list on the <emph>First Group</emph> page, select a column by its label. Entries in the cell range from step 1 will be grouped and sorted by matching values in this column."
msgstr "ໃນລາຍການ <emph>ຈັດກຸ່ມໂດຍ</emph> ຢູ່ໜ້າ <emph>ກຸ່ມທີໜຶ່ງ</emph>, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຖັນຕາມຫົວຂໍ້ຂອງມັນ. ຂໍ້ມູນໃນຊ່ວງເຊວຈາກຂັ້ນຕອນທີ 1 ຈະຖືກຈັດກຸ່ມ ແລະ ຈັດລຽງຕາມຄ່າທີ່ກົງກັນໃນຖັນນີ້."

#. QmNL9
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"par_id451585177625978\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>Calculate subtotals for</emph> box on the <emph>First Group</emph> page, select a column containing values to be subtotaled. If you later change values in this column, Calc will automatically recalculate the subtotals."
msgstr "ໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ຄຳນວນຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍສຳລັບ</emph> ຢູ່ໜ້າ <emph>ກຸ່ມທີໜຶ່ງ</emph>, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຖັນທີ່ມີຄ່າທີ່ຈະເຮັດຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍ. ຖ້າທ່ານປ່ຽນຄ່າໃນຖັນນີ້ໃນພາຍຫຼັງ, Calc ຈະຄຳນວນຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍໃຫ້ໃໝ່ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. CQ9km
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"par_id661585177644535\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>Use function</emph> box on the <emph>First Group</emph> page, select a function to calculate the subtotals for the column selected in step 4."
msgstr "ໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ໃຊ້ຟັງຊັນ</emph> ຢູ່ໜ້າ <emph>ກຸ່ມທີໜຶ່ງ</emph>, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຟັງຊັນເພື່ອຄຳນວນຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍສຳລັບຖັນທີ່ເລືອກໃນຂັ້ນຕອນທີ 4."

#. 3eTTE
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"par_id351585177661529\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Repeat steps 4 and 5 to create subtotals for other columns on the <emph>First Group</emph> page."
msgstr "ເຮັດຊ້ຳຂັ້ນຕອນທີ 4 ແລະ 5 ເພື່ອສ້າງຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍສຳລັບຖັນອື່ນໆໃນໜ້າ <emph>ກຸ່ມທີໜຶ່ງ</emph>."

#. 6GLDr
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"par_id511585177679372\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can create two more subtotal categories by using the <emph>Second Group</emph> and <emph>Third Group</emph> pages and repeating steps 3 to 6. If you do not want to add more groups, then leave the Group by list for each page set to “- none -”."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງປະເພດຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍເພີ່ມອີກສອງປະເພດໂດຍໃຊ້ໜ້າ <emph>ກຸ່ມທີສອງ</emph> ແລະ <emph>ກຸ່ມທີສາມ</emph> ແລະ ເຮັດຊ້ຳຂັ້ນຕອນທີ 3 ຫາ 6. ຖ້າທ່ານບໍ່ຕ້ອງການເພີ່ມກຸ່ມອີກ, ໃຫ້ຕັ້ງລາຍການ ຈັດກຸ່ມໂດຍ ໃນແຕ່ລະໜ້າເປັນ “- ບໍ່ມີ -”."

#. HDB52
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"par_id301585177698777\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click <emph>OK</emph>. Calc will add subtotal and grand total rows to your cell range."
msgstr "ຄລິກ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>. Calc ຈະເພີ່ມແຖວຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍ ແລະ ຜົນລວມທັງໝົດລົງໃນຊ່ວງເຊວຂອງທ່ານ."

#. iMTer
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"hd_id211585178799496\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Subtotal outline"
msgstr "ໂຄງຮ່າງຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍ"

#. 35yNv
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"par_id841585178819108\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you use the Subtotals tool, Calc inserts an outline to the left of the row number column. This outline represents the hierarchical structure of your subtotals, and can be used to hide or show data at different levels in the hierarchy using the numbered column indicators at the top of the outline or the group indicators, denoted by plus <emph>(+)</emph> and minus <emph>(-)</emph> signs."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງມືຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍ, Calc ຈະແຊກໂຄງຮ່າງທາງດ້ານຊ້າຍຂອງຖັນໝາຍເລກແຖວ. ໂຄງຮ່າງນີ້ສະແດງເຖິງໂຄງສ້າງຕາມລຳດັບຊັ້ນຂອງຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍຂອງທ່ານ, ແລະ ສາມາດໃຊ້ເພື່ອເຊື່ອງ ຫຼື ສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນໃນລະດັບຕ່າງໆ ໂດຍໃຊ້ຕົວຊີ້ບອກຕົວເລກຢູ່ເທິງສຸດຂອງໂຄງຮ່າງ ຫຼື ຕົວຊີ້ບອກກຸ່ມ ທີ່ສະແດງດ້ວຍເຄື່ອງໝາຍ ບວກ <emph>(+)</emph> ແລະ ລົບ <emph>(-)</emph>."

#. EhreW
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"par_id371585181820075\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This feature is useful if you have many subtotals, as you can simply hide low-level details, such as individual entries, to produce a high-level summary of your data."
msgstr "ຄຸນສົມບັດນີ້ມີປະໂຫຍດຖ້າທ່ານມີຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍຫຼາຍ, ເພາະທ່ານສາມາດເຊື່ອງລາຍລະອຽດລະດັບຕ່ຳ ເຊັ່ນ ລາຍການຍ່ອຍ, ເພື່ອສ້າງບົດສະຫຼຸບຂໍ້ມູນໃນລະດັບສູງ."

#. C97jN
#: subtotaltool.xhp
msgctxt ""
"subtotaltool.xhp\n"
"par_id161585178829165\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To turn off outlines, choose <menuitem>Data - Group and Outline - Remove Outline</menuitem>. To reinstate them, choose <menuitem>Data - Group and Outline - AutoOutline</menuitem>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອປິດໂຄງຮ່າງ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <menuitem>ຂໍ້ມູນ - ກຸ່ມ ແລະ ໂຄງຮ່າງ - ລຶບໂຄງຮ່າງອອກ</menuitem>. ເພື່ອນຳພວກມັນກັບຄືນມາ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <menuitem>ຂໍ້ມູນ - ກຸ່ມ ແລະ ໂຄງຮ່າງ - ໂຄງຮ່າງອັດຕະໂນມັດ</menuitem>."

#. oU9ew
#: super_subscript.xhp
msgctxt ""
"super_subscript.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Text Superscript / Subscript"
msgstr "ຕົວຂຶ້ນ / ຕົວຫ້ອຍ ຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ"

#. N93BJ
#: super_subscript.xhp
msgctxt ""
"super_subscript.xhp\n"
"bm_id3151112\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>superscript text in cells</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>subscript text in cells</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>cells; text super/sub</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>characters;superscript/subscript</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົວຂຶ້ນໃນເຊວ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົວຫ້ອຍໃນເຊວ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ເຊວ; ຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົວຂຶ້ນ/ຕົວຫ້ອຍ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຕົວອັກສອນ;ຕົວຂຶ້ນ/ຕົວຫ້ອຍ</bookmark_value>"

#. qZkGz
#: super_subscript.xhp
msgctxt ""
"super_subscript.xhp\n"
"hd_id3151112\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"super_subscript\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/super_subscript.xhp\">Text Superscript / Subscript</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"super_subscript\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/super_subscript.xhp\">ຕົວຂຶ້ນ / ຕົວຫ້ອຍ ຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ</link></variable>"

#. DSxqD
#: super_subscript.xhp
msgctxt ""
"super_subscript.xhp\n"
"par_id3154684\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the cell, select the character that you want to put in superscript or subscript."
msgstr "ໃນເຊວ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເຮັດເປັນຕົວຂຶ້ນ ຫຼື ຕົວຫ້ອຍ."

#. CWCc3
#: super_subscript.xhp
msgctxt ""
"super_subscript.xhp\n"
"par_id3150439\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If, for example, you want to write H20 with a subscript 2, select the 2 in the cell (not in the input line)."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການຂຽນ H2O ໂດຍໃຫ້ເລກ 2 ເປັນຕົວຫ້ອຍ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກເລກ 2 ໃນເຊວ (ບໍ່ແມ່ນໃນແຖບປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນ)."

#. HfLPV
#: super_subscript.xhp
msgctxt ""
"super_subscript.xhp\n"
"par_id3149260\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open the context menu for the selected character and choose <emph>Character</emph>. You will see the <emph>Character</emph> dialog."
msgstr "ເປີດເມນູຄລິກຂວາສຳລັບຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ເລືອກ ແລ້ວເລືອກ <emph>ຕົວອັກສອນ</emph>. ທ່ານຈະເຫັນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ຕົວອັກສອນ</emph>."

#. B8gYB
#: super_subscript.xhp
msgctxt ""
"super_subscript.xhp\n"
"par_id3153142\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the <emph>Font Position</emph> tab."
msgstr "ຄລິກທີ່ແຖບ <emph>ຕຳແໜ່ງຟອນ</emph>."

#. 2perr
#: super_subscript.xhp
msgctxt ""
"super_subscript.xhp\n"
"par_id3153954\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the <emph>Subscript</emph> option and click OK."
msgstr "ເລືອກຕົວເລືອກ <emph>ຕົວຫ້ອຍ</emph> ແລ້ວຄລິກ ຕົກລົງ."

#. eqGzu
#: super_subscript.xhp
msgctxt ""
"super_subscript.xhp\n"
"par_id3153876\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/01/05020500.xhp\">Context menu - Character - Font Position</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/01/05020500.xhp\">ເມນູຄລິກຂວາ - ຕົວອັກສອນ - ຕຳແໜ່ງຟອນ</link>"

#. 2wVQM
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Merge and Unmerge Cells"
msgstr "ຮວມ ແລະ ແຍກເຊວ"

#. FFV5z
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"bm_id501632012952361\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>merge/merging cells</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>unmerge/unmerging cells</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>split/splitting cells</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຮວມ/ການຮວມເຊວ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ແຍກ/ການແຍກເຊວ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ແບ່ງ/ການແບ່ງເຊວ</bookmark_value>"

#. T5RbK
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"hd_id8005005\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"table_cellmerge\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/table_cellmerge.xhp\">Merge and Unmerge Cells</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"table_cellmerge\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/table_cellmerge.xhp\">ຮວມ ແລະ ແຍກເຊວ</link></variable>"

#. Hht67
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id8049867\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can select a range of cells, then merge them into a single cell. Conversely, you can take a previously merged cell and divide it back into individual cells."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກຊ່ວງເຊວ, ແລ້ວຮວມພວກມັນເຂົ້າເປັນເຊວດຽວ. ໃນທາງກົງກັນຂ້າມ, ທ່ານສາມາດແຍກເຊວທີ່ເຄີຍຮວມໄວ້ແລ້ວກັບຄືນເປັນເຊວແຍກກັນຄືເກົ່າ."

#. vFF3v
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id0509200913480176\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you copy cells into a target range containing merged cells, the target range gets unmerged first, then the copied cells are pasted in. If the copied cells are merged cells, they retain their merge state."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານຄັດລອກເຊວໄປໃສ່ຊ່ວງເປົ້າໝາຍທີ່ມີເຊວທີ່ຮວມກັນຢູ່, ຊ່ວງເປົ້າໝາຍຈະຖືກແຍກອອກກ່ອນ, ຈາກນັ້ນເຊວທີ່ຄັດລອກມາຈຶ່ງຈະຖືກວາງລົງ. ຖ້າເຊວທີ່ຄັດລອກມາເປັນເຊວທີ່ຮວມກັນ, ພວກມັນຈະຍັງຄົງສະຖານະການຮວມນັ້ນໄວ້."

#. F4ADr
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"hd_id235602\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Merge Cells"
msgstr "ຮວມເຊວ"

#. PhwAW
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id1272927\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click and drag to select the cells to be merged then do one of the following:"
msgstr "ຄລິກ ແລະ ລາກເພື່ອເລືອກເຊວທີ່ຈະຮວມກັນ ຈາກນັ້ນໃຫ້ເຮັດຢ່າງໃດຢ່າງໜຶ່ງດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. BpCih
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id221632803290526\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the Formatting toolbar click:"
msgstr "ໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມືຮູບແບບ ໃຫ້ຄລິກ:"

#. tc6Dw
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id3154351\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Or, right click the selection to open the context menu and choose <menuitem>Merge Cells</menuitem>.<br/>If <menuitem>Unmerge Cells</menuitem> is present instead then the cell selection contains merged cells and cannot be merged further."
msgstr "ຫຼື, ຄລິກຂວາໃສ່ສິ່ງທີ່ເລືອກເພື່ອເປີດເມນູຄລິກຂວາ ແລ້ວເລືອກ <menuitem>ຮວມເຊວ</menuitem>.<br/>ຖ້າເຫັນ <menuitem>ແຍກເຊວ</menuitem> ແທນ, ສະແດງວ່າໃນສ່ວນທີ່ເລືອກມີເຊວທີ່ຮວມກັນຢູ່ແລ້ວ ແລະ ບໍ່ສາມາດຮວມຕື່ມໄດ້ອີກ."

#. uH6dA
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id931632803442925\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Or, in the <emph>Properties</emph> sidebar mark the <emph>Merge Cells</emph> checkbox."
msgstr "ຫຼື, ໃນແຖບຂ້າງ <emph>ຄຸນສົມບັດ</emph> ໃຫ້ໝາຍຕິກໃສ່ຊ່ອງ <emph>ຮວມເຊວ</emph>."

#. fAjCD
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id3154020\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Or, choose <menuitem>Format - Merge and Unmerge Cells - Merge Cells</menuitem>"
msgstr "ຫຼື, ເລືອກ <menuitem>ຮູບແບບ - ຮວມ ແລະ ແຍກເຊວ - ຮວມເຊວ</menuitem>"

#. 6VxQA
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id6424146\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Or, choose <menuitem>Format - Merge and Unmerge Cells - Merge and Center Cells</menuitem>"
msgstr "ຫຼື, ເລືອກ <menuitem>ຮູບແບບ - ຮວມ ແລະ ແຍກເຊວ - ຮວມ ແລະ ຈັດຂໍ້ຄວາມໄວ້ກາງເຊວ</menuitem>"

#. sHLpi
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id961632012538771\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The cells will be merged and the content will be centered in the merged cell."
msgstr "ເຊວຈະຖືກຮວມເຂົ້າກັນ ແລະ ເນື້ອໃນຈະຖືກຈັດໄວ້ເຄິ່ງກາງໃນເຊວທີ່ຮວມແລ້ວນັ້ນ."

#. ULMQA
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"hd_id451368\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Unmerge Cells"
msgstr "ແຍກເຊວ"

#. 2xrnM
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id7116611\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the cell to be unmerged, or a selection that includes the cells to be unmerged then do one of the following:"
msgstr "ເລືອກເຊວທີ່ຈະແຍກ, ຫຼື ສ່ວນທີ່ເລືອກເຊິ່ງລວມມີເຊວທີ່ຈະແຍກ ຈາກນັ້ນໃຫ້ເຮັດຢ່າງໃດຢ່າງໜຶ່ງດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. CmALo
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id581632820903635\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the Formatting toolbar, click:"
msgstr "ໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມືຮູບແບບ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກ:"

#. 4TYCy
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id431632277778130\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Or, right click the selection to open the context menu and choose <menuitem>Unmerge Cells</menuitem>.<br/>If <menuitem>Merge Cells</menuitem> is present instead then the selection does not contain any merged cells."
msgstr "ຫຼື, ຄລິກຂວາໃສ່ສ່ວນທີ່ເລືອກເພື່ອເປີດເມນູຄລິກຂວາ ແລ້ວເລືອກ <menuitem>ແຍກເຊວ</menuitem>.<br/>ຖ້າເຫັນ <menuitem>ຮວມເຊວ</menuitem> ແທນ, ສະແດງວ່າໃນສ່ວນທີ່ເລືອກບໍ່ມີເຊວໃດທີ່ຮວມກັນຢູ່."

#. LrAis
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id261632277824041\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Or, in the <emph>Properties</emph> sidebar clear the <emph>Merge Cells</emph> checkbox."
msgstr "ຫຼື, ໃນແຖບຂ້າງ <emph>ຄຸນສົມບັດ</emph> ໃຫ້ຍົກເລີກການໝາຍຕິກໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ຮວມເຊວ</emph>."

#. uiNiD
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id9493087\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Or, choose <menuitem>Format - Merge and Unmerge Cells - Unmerge Cells</menuitem>."
msgstr "ຫຼື, ເລືອກ <menuitem>ຮູບແບບ - ຮວມ ແລະ ແຍກເຊວ - ແຍກເຊວ</menuitem>."

#. HJEzN
#: table_cellmerge.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_cellmerge.xhp\n"
"par_id561632820960500\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Or, toggle <menuitem>Format - Merge and Unmerge Cells - Merge and Center Cells</menuitem>"
msgstr "ຫຼື, ກົດປ່ຽນສະຖານະ <menuitem>ຮູບແບບ - ຮວມ ແລະ ແຍກເຊວ - ຮວມ ແລະ ຈັດຂໍ້ຄວາມໄວ້ກາງເຊວ</menuitem>"

#. u5xXE
#: table_rotate.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_rotate.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Rotating Tables (Transposing)"
msgstr "ການໝຸນຕາຕະລາງ (ການສະລັບແຖວ ແລະ ຖັນ)"

#. NWEK2
#: table_rotate.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_rotate.xhp\n"
"bm_id3154346\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>tables; transposing</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>transposing tables</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>inverting tables</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>swapping tables</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>columns; swap with rows</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>rows; swapping with columns</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>tables; rotating</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>rotating; tables</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຕາຕະລາງ; ການສະລັບແຖວ ແລະ ຖັນ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການສະລັບແຖວ ແລະ ຖັນຕາຕະລາງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການປີ້ນຕາຕະລາງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການສະລັບຕາຕະລາງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຖັນ; ສະລັບກັບແຖວ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ແຖວ; ສະລັບກັບຖັນ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຕາຕະລາງ; ການໝຸນ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການໝຸນ; ຕາຕະລາງ</bookmark_value>"

#. TZEJK
#: table_rotate.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_rotate.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154346\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"table_rotate\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/table_rotate.xhp\">Rotating Tables (Transposing)</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"table_rotate\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/table_rotate.xhp\">ການໝຸນຕາຕະລາງ (ການສະລັບແຖວ ແລະ ຖັນ)</link></variable>"

#. fzyoE
#: table_rotate.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_rotate.xhp\n"
"par_id3154013\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In $[officename] Calc, there is a way to \"rotate\" a spreadsheet so that rows become columns and columns become rows."
msgstr "ໃນ $[officename] Calc, ມີວິທີ \"ໝຸນ\" ສະເປຣດຊີດ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ແຖວກາຍເປັນຖັນ ແລະ ຖັນກາຍເປັນແຖວ."

#. MXbrh
#: table_rotate.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_rotate.xhp\n"
"par_id3153142\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the cell range that you want to transpose."
msgstr "ເລືອກຊ່ວງເຊວທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການສະລັບແຖວ ແລະ ຖັນ."

#. uS47V
#: table_rotate.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_rotate.xhp\n"
"par_id3153191\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Edit - Cut</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂ - ຕັດ</emph>."

#. MNeBn
#: table_rotate.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_rotate.xhp\n"
"par_id3148575\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the cell that is to be the top left cell in the result."
msgstr "ຄລິກໃສ່ເຊວທີ່ຈະໃຫ້ເປັນເຊວມຸມຊ້າຍເທິງສຸດຂອງຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ."

#. rhSEj
#: table_rotate.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_rotate.xhp\n"
"par_id3156286\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Edit - Paste Special</emph>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂ - ວາງແບບພິເສດ</emph>."

#. cAADF
#: table_rotate.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_rotate.xhp\n"
"par_id3144764\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the dialog, mark <emph>Paste all</emph> and <emph>Transpose</emph>."
msgstr "ໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ, ໃຫ້ໝາຍຕິກໃສ່ <emph>ວາງທັງໝົດ</emph> ແລະ <emph>ສະລັບແຖວ ແລະ ຖັນ (Transpose)</emph>."

#. nFUUg
#: table_rotate.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_rotate.xhp\n"
"par_id3155600\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you now click OK the columns and rows are transposed."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຄລິກ ຕົກລົງ, ຖັນ ແລະ ແຖວຈະຖືກສະລັບກັນ."

#. 2XdS2
#: table_rotate.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_rotate.xhp\n"
"par_id3146969\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/01/02070000.xhp\">Paste Special</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/01/02070000.xhp\">ວາງແບບພິເສດ</link>"

#. qWjQg
#: table_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_view.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Changing Table Views"
msgstr "ການປ່ຽນມຸມມອງຕາຕະລາງ"

#. dmkBp
#: table_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_view.xhp\n"
"bm_id3147304\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>row headers; hiding</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>column headers; hiding</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>tables; views</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>views; tables</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>grids;hiding lines in sheets</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>hiding;headers/grid lines</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>changing;table views</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຫົວແຖວ; ການເຊື່ອງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຫົວຖັນ; ການເຊື່ອງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຕາຕະລາງ; ມຸມມອງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ມຸມມອງ; ຕາຕະລາງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ເສັ້ນຕາຕະລາງ;ການເຊື່ອງເສັ້ນໃນແຜ່ນງານ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການເຊື່ອງ;ຫົວຂໍ້/ເສັ້ນຕາຕະລາງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການປ່ຽນແປງ;ມຸມມອງຕາຕະລາງ</bookmark_value>"

#. t4Dpn
#: table_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_view.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147304\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"table_view\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/table_view.xhp\">Changing Table Views</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"table_view\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/table_view.xhp\">ການປ່ຽນມຸມມອງຕາຕະລາງ</link></variable>"

#. Fnu8g
#: table_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_view.xhp\n"
"par_id3153192\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To hide column and line headers in a table:"
msgstr "ເພື່ອເຊື່ອງຫົວຖັນ ແລະ ຫົວແຖວໃນຕາຕະລາງ:"

#. dmh8o
#: table_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_view.xhp\n"
"par_id3153768\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Under the menu item <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Calc,</emph> go to the <emph>View</emph> tab page. Unmark<emph> Column/row headers</emph>. Confirm with <emph>OK</emph>."
msgstr "ພາຍໃຕ້ເມນູ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Calc,</emph> ໄປທີ່ແຖບ <emph>ມຸມມອງ (View)</emph>. ຍົກເລີກການໝາຍຕິກໃນ <emph>ຫົວຖັນ/ແຖວ</emph>. ຢືນຢັນດ້ວຍການກົດ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>."

#. AXeqh
#: table_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_view.xhp\n"
"par_id3147436\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To hide grid lines:"
msgstr "ເພື່ອເຊື່ອງເສັ້ນຕາຕະລາງ (Grid lines):"

#. XDpAC
#: table_view.xhp
msgctxt ""
"table_view.xhp\n"
"par_id3153726\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Under the menu item <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Calc</emph>, go to the <emph>View</emph> tab page. Choose <emph>Hide</emph> in the <emph>Grid lines</emph> dropdown. Confirm with <emph>OK</emph>."
msgstr "ພາຍໃຕ້ເມນູ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Calc</emph>, ໄປທີ່ແຖບ <emph>ມຸມມອງ (View)</emph>. ເລືອກ <emph>ເຊື່ອງ</emph> ໃນລາຍການ <emph>ເສັ້ນຕາຕະລາງ</emph>. ຢືນຢັນດ້ວຍການກົດ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>."

