msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3156283\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For each cell, you can define entries to be valid. Invalid entries to a cell will be rejected."
msgstr "ສຳລັບແຕ່ລະເຊວ, ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດລາຍການທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງໄດ້. ລາຍການທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງທີ່ປ້ອນລົງໃນເຊວຈະຖືກປະຕິເສດ."

#. cbHnL
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3145252\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The validity rule is activated when a new value is entered. If an invalid value has already been inserted into the cell, or if you insert a value in the cell either with drag-and-drop or by copying and pasting, the validity rule will not take effect."
msgstr "ກົດລະບຽບຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງຈະເຮັດວຽກເມື່ອມີການປ້ອນຄ່າໃໝ່. ຖ້າມີຄ່າທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງຖືກໃສ່ໄວ້ໃນເຊວແລ້ວ, ຫຼື ຖ້າທ່ານໃສ່ຄ່າໃນເຊວດ້ວຍການລາກ-ວາງ ຫຼື ຄັດລອກ-ວາງ, ກົດລະບຽບຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງຈະບໍ່ມີຜົນ."

#. N7bP8
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id5174718\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can choose <emph>Tools - Detective</emph> at any time and choose the command <link href=\"text/scalc/01/06030800.xhp\"><emph>Mark Invalid Data</emph></link> to display which cells contain invalid values."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກ <emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ການກວດສອບ</emph> ເວລາໃດກໍໄດ້ ແລະ ເລືອກຄຳສັ່ງ <link href=\"text/scalc/01/06030800.xhp\"><emph>ໝາຍຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ</emph></link> ເພື່ອສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນວ່າເຊວໃດທີ່ມີຄ່າບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. vExqw
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155603\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Using Cell Contents Validity"
msgstr "ການໃຊ້ການກວດສອບຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງຂອງເນື້ອໃນເຊວ"

#. vPWZE
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3155959\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the cells for which you want to define a new validity rule."
msgstr "ເລືອກເຊວທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການກຳນົດກົດລະບຽບຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງໃໝ່."

#. Rxqr5
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3148837\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <item type=\"menuitem\">Data - Validity</item>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ຂໍ້ມູນ - ຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງ</item>."

#. BCtiM
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3156020\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the <emph>Criteria</emph> tab page, enter the conditions for new values entered into cells."
msgstr "ໃນແຖບ <emph>ເງື່ອນໄຂ</emph>, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນເງື່ອນໄຂສຳລັບຄ່າໃໝ່ທີ່ຈະປ້ອນລົງໃນເຊວ."

#. 6t74m
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3159208\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the <emph>Allow</emph> field, select an option."
msgstr "ໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ອະນຸຍາດ</emph>, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຕົວເລືອກໃດໜຶ່ງ."

#. xDJjD
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3153011\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you select \"Whole Numbers\", values such as \"12.5\" are not allowed. Choosing \"Date\" allows date information both in the local date format as well as in the form of a <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03030101.xhp\">serial date</link>. Similarly, the \"Time\" condition permits time values such as \"12:00\" or serial time numbers. \"Text Length\" stipulates that cells are allowed to contain text only."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກ \"ຈຳນວນຖ້ວນ\", ຄ່າເຊັ່ນ \"12.5\" ຈະບໍ່ຖືກອະນຸຍາດ. ການເລືອກ \"ວັນທີ\" ຈະອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນວັນທີທັງໃນຮູບແບບວັນທີທ້ອງຖິ່ນ ແລະ ໃນຮູບແບບ <link href=\"text/sbasic/shared/03030101.xhp\">ເລກລຳດັບວັນທີ</link>. ເຊັ່ນດຽວກັນ, ເງື່ອນໄຂ \"ເວລາ\" ຈະອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ປ້ອນຄ່າເວລາ ເຊັ່ນ \"12:00\" ຫຼື ເລກລຳດັບເວລາ. \"ຄວາມຍາວຂໍ້ຄວາມ\" ຈະກຳນົດໃຫ້ເຊວບັນຈຸໄດ້ສະເພາະຂໍ້ຄວາມເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. qGjDb
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id9224829\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select \"List\" to enter a list of valid entries."
msgstr "ເລືອກ \"ລາຍການ\" ເພື່ອປ້ອນລາຍການຂອງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. JB7oA
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3149317\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the next condition under <emph>Data</emph>. According to what you choose, additional options will be selectable."
msgstr "ເລືອກເງື່ອນໄຂຖັດໄປພາຍໃຕ້ <emph>ຂໍ້ມູນ</emph>. ອີງຕາມສິ່ງທີ່ທ່ານເລືອກ, ຈະມີຕົວເລືອກເພີ່ມເຕີມໃຫ້ເລືອກໄດ້."

#. KD7kV
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3151389\n"
"help.text"
msgid "After you have determined the conditions for cell validity, you can use the other two tab pages to create message boxes:"
msgstr "ຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ກຳນົດເງື່ອນໄຂສຳລັບຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງຂອງເຊວແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ແຖບອີກສອງແຖບທີ່ເຫຼືອເພື່ອສ້າງກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ:"

#. 6aBi5
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3159261\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the <emph>Input Help</emph> tab page, enter the title and the text of the tip, which will then be displayed if the cell is selected."
msgstr "ໃນແຖບ <emph>ການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອການປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນ</emph>, ໃຫ້ປ້ອນຫົວຂໍ້ ແລະ ຂໍ້ຄວາມແນະນຳ, ເຊິ່ງຈະສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນເມື່ອເຊວນັ້ນຖືກເລືອກ."

#. U3y7G
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3156396\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the <emph>Error Alert</emph> tab page, select the action to be carried out in the event of an error."
msgstr "ໃນແຖບ <emph>ການແຈ້ງເຕືອນຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ</emph>, ໃຫ້ເລືອກການກະທຳທີ່ຈະໃຫ້ລະບົບເຮັດເມື່ອເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ."

#. JDuqF
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3147416\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you select \"Stop\" as the action, invalid entries are not accepted, and the previous cell contents are retained."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກ \"ຢຸດ (Stop)\" ເປັນການກະທຳ, ລາຍການທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງຈະບໍ່ຖືກຍອມຮັບ, ແລະ ເນື້ອໃນເດີມຂອງເຊວຈະຖືກຮັກສາໄວ້."

#. FeWnd
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3150033\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select \"Warning\" or \"Information\" to display a dialog in which the entry can either be canceled or accepted."
msgstr "ເລືອກ \"ຄຳເຕືອນ\" ຫຼື \"ຂໍ້ມູນ\" ເພື່ອສະແດງປ່ອງຢ້ຽມທີ່ສາມາດເລືອກໄດ້ວ່າຈະຍົກເລີກ ຫຼື ຍອມຮັບສິ່ງທີ່ປ້ອນລົງໄປ."

#. 9aCdk
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3149947\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you select \"Macro\", then by using the <emph>Browse</emph> button you can specify a macro to be run in the event of an error."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກ \"ມາກໂຄ\", ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ <emph>ເລືອກເບິ່ງ</emph> ເພື່ອກຳນົດມາກໂຄທີ່ຈະໃຫ້ເຮັດວຽກເມື່ອເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ."

#. eiEtj
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3149011\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To display the error message, select <link href=\"text/scalc/01/12120300.xhp\">Show error message when invalid values are entered</link>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອສະແດງຂໍ້ຄວາມຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <link href=\"text/scalc/01/12120300.xhp\">ສະແດງຂໍ້ຄວາມຂໍ້ຜິດພາດເມື່ອມີການປ້ອນຄ່າທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ</link>."

#. VTfnE
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3148586\n"
"help.text"
msgid "After changing the action for a cell on the <emph>Error Alert</emph> tab page and closing the dialog with OK, you must first select another cell before the change takes effect."
msgstr "ຫຼັງຈາກປ່ຽນແປງການກະທຳສຳລັບເຊວໃນແຖບ <emph>ການແຈ້ງເຕືອນຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ</emph> ແລະ ປິດປ່ອງຢ້ຽມດ້ວຍການກົດ ຕົກລົງ ແລ້ວ, ທ່ານຕ້ອງເລືອກເຊວອື່ນກ່ອນການປ່ຽນແປງນັ້ນຈຶ່ງຈະມີຜົນ."

#. PpEfP
#: validity.xhp
msgctxt ""
"validity.xhp\n"
"par_id3154805\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/12120000.xhp\">Data - Validity</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/12120000.xhp\">ຂໍ້ມູນ - ຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງ</link>"

#. cEdPu
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Naming Cells"
msgstr "ການຕັ້ງຊື່ເຊວ"

#. DGAwD
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"bm_id3147434\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>cells; defining names</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>names; defining for cells</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>values; defining names</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>constants definition</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>variables; defining names</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>cell ranges; defining names</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>defining;names for cell ranges</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>formulas; defining names</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>addressing; by defined names</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>cell names; defining/addressing</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>references; by defined names</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>allowed cell names</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>renaming;cells</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ເຊວ; ການກຳນົດຊື່</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ຊື່; ການກຳນົດສຳລັບເຊວ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ຄ່າ; ການກຳນົດຊື່</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ການກຳນົດຄ່າຄົງທີ່</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ຕົວປ່ຽນ; ການກຳນົດຊື່</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ຊ່ວງເຊວ; ການກຳນົດຊື່</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ການກຳນົດ;ຊື່ສຳລັບຊ່ວງເຊວ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ສູດ; ການກຳນົດຊື່</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ການອ້າງອີງ; ໂດຍຊື່ທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ຊື່ເຊວ; ການກຳນົດ/ການອ້າງອີງ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ການອ້າງອີງ; ໂດຍຊື່ທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ຊື່ເຊວທີ່ອະນຸຍາດ</bookmark_value>      <bookmark_value>ການປ່ຽນຊື່;ເຊວ</bookmark_value>"

#. vT4C3
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147434\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"value_with_name\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/value_with_name.xhp\">Naming Cells</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"value_with_name\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/value_with_name.xhp\">ການຕັ້ງຊື່ເຊວ</link></variable>"

#. EyNmi
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"hd_id4391918\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Allowed names"
msgstr "ຊື່ທີ່ອະນຸຍາດ"

#. MECFu
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id2129581\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Names in Calc can contain letters, numeric characters, and the underline character. Names must start with a letter or an underline character."
msgstr "ຊື່ໃນ Calc ສາມາດມີຕົວອັກສອນ, ຕົວເລກ, ແລະ ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຂີດກ້ອງ. ຊື່ຕ້ອງເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນ ຫຼື ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຂີດກ້ອງເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. GztrF
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id1120029\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Allowed special characters:"
msgstr "ຕົວອັກສອນພິເສດທີ່ອະນຸຍາດ:"

#. 4VANL
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id3362224\n"
"help.text"
msgid "underline (_)"
msgstr "ຂີດກ້ອງ (_)"

#. BvnNt
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id328989\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Names must not be the same as cell references. For example, the name A1 is invalid because A1 is a cell reference to the top left cell."
msgstr "ຊື່ຕ້ອງບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັບການອ້າງອີງເຊວ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຊື່ A1 ແມ່ນໃຊ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ ເພາະ A1 ແມ່ນການອ້າງອີງຫາເຊວມຸມຊ້າຍເທິງສຸດ."

#. ufHkJ
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id32898987\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Names must not start with the letters C or R followed by a number; also single characters C and R are not allowed as names. See the ADDRESS function for more information."
msgstr "ຊື່ຕ້ອງບໍ່ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນ C ຫຼື R ທີ່ຕາມດ້ວຍຕົວເລກ; ນອກຈາກນັ້ນ, ຕົວອັກສອນ C ແລະ R ຕົວດຽວກໍບໍ່ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ໃຊ້ເປັນຊື່. ເບິ່ງຟັງຊັນ ADDRESS ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມ."

#. 6piLZ
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id4769737\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Names for cell ranges must not include blanks. Blanks are allowed within names for sheets and documents."
msgstr "ຊື່ສຳລັບຊ່ວງເຊວຕ້ອງບໍ່ມີການຍະວ່າງ. ແຕ່ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ມະຍະວ່າງໄດ້ໃນຊື່ຂອງແຜ່ນງານ ແລະ ເອກະສານ."

#. wNYEr
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"hd_id1226233\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"naming_cells\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/value_with_name.xhp#naming cells and ranges\">Naming cells and ranges</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"naming_cells\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/value_with_name.xhp#naming cells and ranges\">ການຕັ້ງຊື່ເຊວ ແລະ ຊ່ວງເຊວ</link></variable>"

#. FPo7Y
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id5489364\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A good way of making the references to cells and cell ranges in formulas legible is to give the ranges names. For example, you can name the range A1:B2 <emph>Start</emph>. You can then write a formula such as \"=SUM(Start)\". Even after you insert or delete rows or columns, $[officename] still correctly assigns the ranges identified by name. Range names must not contain any spaces."
msgstr "ວິທີທີ່ດີທີ່ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ການອ້າງອີງເຊວ ແລະ ຊ່ວງເຊວໃນສູດອ່ານງ່າຍຂຶ້ນແມ່ນການຕັ້ງຊື່ໃຫ້ພວກມັນ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ທ່ານສາມາດຕັ້ງຊື່ຊ່ວງ A1:B2 ວ່າ <emph>ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ</emph>. ຈາກນັ້ນທ່ານສາມາດຂຽນສູດໄດ້ເຊັ່ນ \"=SUM(ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ)\". ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າທ່ານຈະແຊກ ຫຼື ລຶບແຖວ ຫຼື ຖັນ, $[officename] ຍັງຄົງກຳນົດຊ່ວງຕາມຊື່ນັ້ນໄດ້ຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ. ຊື່ຊ່ວງຕ້ອງບໍ່ມີການຍະວ່າງ."

#. aZZC8
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id953398\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For example, it is much easier to read a formula for sales tax if you can write \"= Amount * Tax_rate\" instead of \"= A5 * B12\". In this case, you would name cell A5 \"Amount\" and cell B12 \"Tax_rate.\""
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ: ມັນຈະອ່ານສູດພາສີການຂາຍໄດ້ງ່າຍກວ່າຫຼາຍຖ້າທ່ານສາມາດຂຽນວ່າ \"= ຈຳນວນ * ອັດຕາພາສີ\" ແທນທີ່ຈະຂຽນວ່າ \"= A5 * B12\". ໃນກໍລະນີນີ້ນ, ທ່ານຈະຕັ້ງຊື່ເຊວ A5 ວ່າ \"ຈຳນວນ\" ແລະ ເຊວ B12 ວ່າ \"ອັດຕາພາສີ\"."

#. LViNz
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id4889675\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the <emph>Define Names</emph> dialog to define names for formulas or parts of formulas you need more often. In order to specify range names,"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ກຳນົດຊື່</emph> ເພື່ອກຳນົດຊື່ສຳລັບສູດ ຫຼື ສ່ວນຂອງສູດທີ່ທ່ານໃຊ້ເລື້ອຍໆ. ເພື່ອກຳນົດຊື່ຊ່ວງ,"

#. UNzu6
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id3153954\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select a cell or range of cells, then choose <emph>Sheet - Named Ranges and Expressions - Define</emph>. The <emph>Define Names</emph> dialog appears."
msgstr "ເລືອກເຊວ ຫຼື ຊ່ວງເຊວ, ຈາກນັ້ນເລືອກ <emph>ແຜ່ນງານ - ຊ່ວງທີ່ຕັ້ງຊື່ ແລະ ສຳນວນ - ກຳນົດ</emph>. ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ກຳນົດຊື່</emph> ຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນ."

#. XRBXG
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id3156283\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Type the name of the selected area in the <emph>Name</emph> field. Click <emph>Add</emph>. The newly defined name appears in the list below. Click OK to close the dialog."
msgstr "ພິມຊື່ຂອງພື້ນທີ່ທີ່ເລືອກໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ຊື່</emph>. ຄລິກ <emph>ເພີ່ມ</emph>. ຊື່ທີ່ກຳນົດໃໝ່ຈະປະກົດໃນລາຍການທາງລຸ່ມ. ຄລິກ ຕົກລົງ ເພື່ອປິດປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ."

#. wehKd
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id5774101\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can also name other cell ranges in this dialog by entering the name in the field and then selecting the respective cells."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດຕັ້ງຊື່ຊ່ວງເຊວອື່ນໆໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມນີ້ໄດ້ ໂດຍການປ້ອນຊື່ລົງໃນຊ່ອງ ແລ້ວເລືອກເຊວທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. 3sCdF
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id3154942\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you type the name in a formula, after the first few characters entered you will see the entire name as a tip."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານພິມຊື່ລົງໃນສູດ, ຫຼັງຈາກພິມສອງສາມຕົວອັກສອນທຳອິດ ທ່ານຈະເຫັນຊື່ເຕັມສະແດງຂຶ້ນມາເປັນຄຳແນະນຳ."

#. SgWa3
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id3154510\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press the Enter key in order to accept the name from the tip."
msgstr "ກົດປຸ່ມ Enter ເພື່ອຍອມຮັບຊື່ຈາກຄຳແນະນຳນັ້ນ."

#. dGV3u
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id3150749\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If more than one name starts with the same characters, you can scroll forward through all the names using the <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> <keycode>+ Tab keys</keycode> and backward using the <keycode>Shift +</keycode> <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> <keycode>+ Tab</keycode> keys."
msgstr "ຖ້າມີຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງຊື່ທີ່ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນດຽວກັນ, ທ່ານສາມາດເລື່ອນເບິ່ງຊື່ທັງໝົດໄປທາງໜ້າໂດຍໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> <keycode>+ Tab</keycode> ແລະ ເລື່ອນຖອຍຫຼັງໂດຍໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ <keycode>Shift +</keycode> <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> <keycode>+ Tab</keycode>."

#. heTpi
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"hd_id881763912898660\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"naming_formulas\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/value_with_name.xhp#naming formulas\">Naming Formulas</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"naming_formulas\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/value_with_name.xhp#naming formulas\">ການຕັ້ງຊື່ສູດ</link></variable>"

#. guYKD
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id501763912916013\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can assign a simpler or more familiar name to a long or complex formula expression."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດຊື່ທີ່ງ່າຍ ຫຼື ຄຸ້ນເຄີຍກວ່າໃຫ້ກັບສຳນວນສູດທີ່ຍາວ ຫຼື ຊັບຊ້ອນ."

#. GHCkL
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id141763911755154\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Sheet - Named Ranges and Expressions - Define</emph>. The <emph>Define Names</emph> dialog appears."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ແຜ່ນງານ - ຊ່ວງທີ່ຕັ້ງຊື່ ແລະ ສຳນວນ - ກຳນົດ</emph>. ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ກຳນົດຊື່</emph> ຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນ."

#. aFBj9
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id201763911835200\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter the name for the formula expression in the <emph>Name</emph> field."
msgstr "ປ້ອນຊື່ສຳລັບສຳນວນສູດໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ຊື່</emph>."

#. vSREF
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id271763912749700\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter the formula expression in the <emph>Range or formula expression</emph> box. For example, if you have named your formula <emph>HYP</emph>, you can enter the expression <input>SQRT(A1*A1 + B1*B1)</input>  to compute the distance between two points on a plane. Do not precede the expression with an equal sign (=)."
msgstr "ປ້ອນສຳນວນສູດລົງໃນຊ່ອງ <emph>ຊ່ວງ ຫຼື ສຳນວນສູດ</emph>. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຖ້າທ່ານຕັ້ງຊື່ສູດວ່າ <emph>HYP</emph>, ທ່ານສາມາດປ້ອນສຳນວນ <input>SQRT(A1*A1 + B1*B1)</input> ເພື່ອຄຳນວນໄລຍະຫ່າງລະຫວ່າງສອງຈຸດໃນລະນາບ. ຫ້າມໃສ່ເຄື່ອງໝາຍເທົ່າກັບ (=) ໄວ້ທາງໜ້າສຳນວນ."

#. mh2cC
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id721763912801530\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click <emph>Add</emph>. The newly defined name appears in the list below. Click OK to close the dialog."
msgstr "ຄລິກ <emph>ເພີ່ມ</emph>. ຊື່ທີ່ກຳນົດໃໝ່ຈະປະກົດໃນລາຍການທາງລຸ່ມ. ຄລິກ ຕົກລົງ ເພື່ອປິດປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ."

#. BiumC
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id401763913780278\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter the name of the named formula in the desired cell. The cell value is the result of the formula expression. For example, enter <input>=HYP()</input>  to compute the formula above.  Note that you cannot directly pass parameters to named formulas."
msgstr "ປ້ອນຊື່ຂອງສູດທີ່ຕັ້ງຊື່ໄວ້ລົງໃນເຊວທີ່ຕ້ອງການ. ຄ່າໃນເຊວຈະເປັນຜົນໄດ້ຮັບຂອງສຳນວນສູດນັ້ນ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ປ້ອນ <input>=HYP()</input> ເພື່ອຄຳນວນສູດຂ້າງເທິງ. ໝາຍເຫດວ່າທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດສົ່ງພາຣາມິເຕີໂດຍກົງໃຫ້ກັບສູດທີ່ຕັ້ງຊື່ໄດ້."

#. 8kfDA
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id911763913184094\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Naming conventions apply to named formulas. Absolute and relative references are respected. For example, when the named formula is copied and pasted."
msgstr "ຫຼັກການຕັ້ງຊື່ກໍນຳໃຊ້ກັບສູດທີ່ຕັ້ງຊື່ຄືກັນ. ລະບົບຈະຮັກສາການອ້າງອີງແບບສຳບູນ ແລະ ແບບທຽບຖານໄວ້ ເຊັ່ນ ເວລາຄັດລອກ ແລະ ວາງສູດທີ່ຕັ້ງຊື່ນັ້ນ."

#. j7cYG
#: value_with_name.xhp
msgctxt ""
"value_with_name.xhp\n"
"par_id3153711\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/04070100.xhp\">Sheet - Named Ranges and Expressions - Define</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/04070100.xhp\">ແຜ່ນງານ - ຊ່ວງທີ່ຕັ້ງຊື່ ແລະ ສຳນວນ - ກຳນົດ</link>"

#. tT8Ku
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Inserting External Data in Table (WebQuery)"
msgstr "ການແຊກຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກໃສ່ໃນຕາຕະລາງ (WebQuery)"

#. eaFpE
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"bm_id3154346\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>HTML WebQuery</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ranges; inserting in tables</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>external data; inserting</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>tables; inserting external data</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>web pages; importing data</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>WebQuery filter</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>inserting; external data</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>data sources; external data</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>HTML WebQuery</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຊ່ວງ; ການແຊກໃນຕາຕະລາງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກ; ການແຊກ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຕາຕະລາງ; ການແຊກຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ເວັບໄຊ; ການນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຕົວຕອງ WebQuery</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການແຊກ; ຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ; ຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກ</bookmark_value>"

#. LzMwA
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"hd_id3125863\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"webquery\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/webquery.xhp\">Inserting External Data in Table (WebQuery)</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"webquery\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/webquery.xhp\">ການແຊກຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກໃສ່ໃນຕາຕະລາງ (WebQuery)</link></variable>"

#. Uf8QW
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3155131\n"
"help.text"
msgid "With the help of the <emph>Web Page Query ($[officename] Calc)</emph> import filter, you can insert tables from HTML documents in a Calc spreadsheet."
msgstr "ດ້ວຍການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຂອງຕົວຕອງການນຳເຂົ້າ <emph>Web Page Query ($[officename] Calc)</emph>, ທ່ານສາມາດແຊກຕາຕະລາງຈາກເອກະສານ HTML ລົງໃນສະເປຣດຊີດ Calc ໄດ້."

#. eBygd
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3148575\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can use the same method to insert ranges defined by name from a Calc or Microsoft Excel spreadsheet."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ວິທີດຽວກັນນີ້ເພື່ອແຊກຊ່ວງທີ່ຕັ້ງຊື່ໄວ້ຈາກສະເປຣດຊີດ Calc ຫຼື Microsoft Excel ໄດ້."

#. odxLF
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3149664\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The following insert methods are available:"
msgstr "ມີວິທີການແຊກດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. kNB42
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"hd_id3146976\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Inserting by Dialog"
msgstr "ການແຊກດ້ວຍປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ"

#. WJEih
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3154319\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Set the cell cursor at the cell where the new content will be inserted."
msgstr "ວາງເຄີເຊີໃນເຊວທີ່ຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ແຊກເນື້ອໃນໃໝ່."

#. SCn3P
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3145750\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Sheet - External Links</emph>. This opens the <link href=\"text/scalc/01/04090000.xhp\">External Data</link> dialog."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <emph>ແຜ່ນງານ - ລິງພາຍນອກ</emph>. ອັນນີ້ຈະເປີດປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <link href=\"text/scalc/01/04090000.xhp\">ຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກ</link>."

#. AGj3g
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3149958\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter the URL of the HTML document or the name of the spreadsheet. Press Enter when finished. Click the <emph>Browse</emph> button to open a file selection dialog."
msgstr "ປ້ອນ URL ຂອງເອກະສານ HTML ຫຼື ຊື່ຂອງສະເປຣດຊີດ. ກົດ Enter ເມື່ອສຳເລັດ. ຄລິກປຸ່ມ <emph>ເລືອກເບິ່ງ</emph> ເພື່ອເປີດປ່ອງຢ້ຽມເລືອກໄຟລ໌."

#. 5b5MC
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3149400\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the large list box of the dialog, select the named ranges or tables you want to insert."
msgstr "ໃນກ່ອງລາຍການຂະໜາດໃຫຍ່ຂອງປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຊ່ວງທີ່ຕັ້ງຊື່ ຫຼື ຕາຕະລາງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແຊກ."

#. Kegfn
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3155064\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can also specify that the ranges or tables are updated every n seconds."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດກຳນົດໃຫ້ຊ່ວງ ຫຼື ຕາຕະລາງນັ້ນອັບເດດທຸກໆ n ວິນາທີ."

#. ywoJU
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3155443\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The import filter can create names for cell ranges on the fly. As much formatting as possible is retained, while the filter intentionally does not load any images."
msgstr "ຕົວຕອງການນຳເຂົ້າສາມາດສ້າງຊື່ສຳລັບຊ່ວງເຊວໄດ້ທັນທີ. ລະບົບຈະຮັກສາຮູບແບບໄວ້ໃຫ້ຫຼາຍທີ່ສຸດເທົ່າທີ່ຈະເຮັດໄດ້, ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຕົວຕອງຈະຕັ້ງໃຈບໍ່ໂຫລດຮູບພາບໃດໆ."

#. HA9v2
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149021\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Inserting by Navigator"
msgstr "ການແຊກດ້ວຍຕົວນຳທາງ"

#. KpQYC
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3153965\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open two documents: the $[officename] Calc spreadsheet in which the external data is to be inserted (target document) and the document from which the external data derives (source document)."
msgstr "ເປີດສອງເອກະສານ: ສະເປຣດຊີດ $[officename] Calc ທີ່ຕ້ອງການແຊກຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກ (ເອກະສານເປົ້າໝາຍ) ແລະ ເອກະສານທີ່ເປັນແຫຼ່ງຂອງຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກ (ເອກະສານຕົ້ນສະບັບ)."

#. pEbXg
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3150205\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the target document open the <link href=\"text/shared/01/navigator.xhp\">Navigator</link>."
msgstr "ໃນເອກະສານເປົ້າໝາຍ, ໃຫ້ເປີດ <link href=\"text/shared/01/navigator.xhp\">ຕົວນຳທາງ (Navigator)</link>."

#. z9DtM
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3152990\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the lower combo box of the Navigator select the source document. The Navigator now shows the range names and database ranges or the tables contained in the source document."
msgstr "ໃນກ່ອງລາຍການທາງລຸ່ມຂອງຕົວນຳທາງ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກເອກະສານຕົ້ນສະບັບ. ຕອນນີ້ຕົວນຳທາງຈະສະແດງຊື່ຊ່ວງ, ຊ່ວງຖານຂໍ້ມູນ ຫຼື ຕາຕະລາງທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນເອກະສານຕົ້ນສະບັບນັ້ນ."

#. HxDHk
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3148842\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the Navigator select the <emph>Insert as link</emph> drag mode<image id=\"img_id3152985\" src=\"sw/res/sc20238.png\" width=\"0.222inch\" height=\"0.222inch\"><alt id=\"alt_id3152985\">Icon</alt></image>."
msgstr "ໃນຕົວນຳທາງ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກໂໝດການລາກ <emph>ແຊກເປັນລິງ</emph> <image id=\"img_id3152985\" src=\"sw/res/sc20238.png\" width=\"0.222inch\" height=\"0.222inch\"><alt id=\"alt_id3152985\">ໄອຄອນ</alt></image>."

#. LS3Wf
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3157978\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Drag the desired external data from the Navigator into the target document."
msgstr "ລາກຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກທີ່ຕ້ອງການຈາກຕົວນຳທາງໄປໃສ່ໃນເອກະສານເປົ້າໝາຍ."

#. 9GfqA
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3144768\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you have loaded an HTML document with the <emph>Web Page Query</emph> filter as the source document, you will find the tables in the Navigator, named continuously from \"HTML_table1\" onwards, and also two range names that have been created:"
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານໄດ້ໂຫລດເອກະສານ HTML ດ້ວຍຕົວຕອງ <emph>Web Page Query</emph> ເປັນເອກະສານຕົ້ນສະບັບ, ທ່ານຈະເຫັນຕາຕະລາງໃນຕົວນຳທາງ ເຊິ່ງຈະຕັ້ງຊື່ຕໍ່ເນື່ອງກັນເລີ່ມຈາກ \"HTML_table1\" ເປັນຕົ້ນໄປ, ແລະ ຍັງມີຊື່ຊ່ວງອີກສອງຊື່ທີ່ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນ:"

#. rcjUt
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3152873\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"literal\">HTML_all</item> - designates the entire document"
msgstr "<item type=\"literal\">HTML_all</item> - ໝາຍເຖິງເອກະສານທັງໝົດ"

#. ecFZG
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3149897\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"literal\">HTML_tables</item> - designates all HTML tables in the document"
msgstr "<item type=\"literal\">HTML_tables</item> - ໝາຍເຖິງຕາຕະລາງ HTML ທັງໝົດໃນເອກະສານ"

#. TGhCr
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149126\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Editing the external data"
msgstr "ການແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກ"

#. GEeyF
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3159228\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Open <emph>Edit - Links</emph>. Here you can edit the link to the external data."
msgstr "ເປີດ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂ - ລິງ</emph>. ບ່ອນນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂລິງທີ່ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຫາຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກໄດ້."

#. xJkAV
#: webquery.xhp
msgctxt ""
"webquery.xhp\n"
"par_id3154650\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/04090000.xhp\">External data dialog</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/04090000.xhp\">ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກ</link>"

#. GnXq4
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Using Wildcards in Formulas"
msgstr "ການໃຊ້ຕົວແທນໃນສູດ"

#. kZVe7
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"bm_id3152149\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>wildcards in formulas</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>wildcards;examples</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຕົວແທນໃນສູດ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ຕົວແທນ;ຕົວຢ່າງ</bookmark_value>"

#. ynEWi
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"hd_id941629155075179\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"wildcards_h1\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/wildcards.xhp\">Using Wildcards in Formulas</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"wildcards_h1\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/wildcards.xhp\">ການໃຊ້ຕົວແທນໃນສູດ</link></variable>"

#. yqMKw
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id571629155308959\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Wildcards are special characters that can be used in search strings that are passed as arguments to some Calc functions. They can also be used to define search criteria in the <emph>Find & Replace</emph> dialog. The use of wildcards enables the definition of more advanced search parameters with a single search string."
msgstr "ຕົວແທນ (Wildcards) ແມ່ນຕົວອັກສອນພິເສດທີ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ໃນຂໍ້ຄວາມຄົ້ນຫາທີ່ຖືກສົ່ງເປັນອາກິວເມນ (arguments) ໃຫ້ກັບບາງຟັງຊັນຂອງ Calc. ພວກມັນຍັງສາມາດໃຊ້ເພື່ອ ກຳນົດເງື່ອນໄຂການຄົ້ນຫາໃນປ່ອງຢ້ຽມ <emph>ຊອກຫາ ແລະ ແທນທີ່</emph>. ການໃຊ້ຕົວແທນຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ສາມາດກຳນົດພາຣາມິເຕີການຄົ້ນຫາທີ່ຂັ້ນສູງຂຶ້ນດ້ວຍຂໍ້ຄວາມຄົ້ນຫາດຽວ."

#. vQrdp
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id391629156224638\n"
"help.text"
msgid "%PRODUCTNAME Calc supports either <emph>wildcards</emph> or <emph>regular expressions</emph> as arguments depending on the current application settings. By default %PRODUCTNAME Calc is set to support wildcards instead of regular expressions."
msgstr "%PRODUCTNAME Calc ຮອງຮັບທັງ <emph>ຕົວແທນ (wildcards)</emph> ຫຼື <emph>ນິພົດປົກກະຕິ (regular expressions)</emph> ເປັນອາກິວເມນ ຂຶ້ນກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າແອັບພລິເຄຊັນປັດຈຸບັນ. ໂດຍຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ %PRODUCTNAME Calc ຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າໃຫ້ຮອງຮັບຕົວແທນແທນນິພົດປົກກະຕິ."

#. GVpD7
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id551629156504794\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To make sure wildcards are supported, go to <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - Calculate</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>Tools - Options - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - Calculate</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline> and check if the option <emph>Enable wildcards in formulas</emph> is selected. Note that you can use this dialog to switch to regular expressions by choosing <emph>Enable regular expressions in formulas</emph> or choose to support neither wildcards nor regular expressions."
msgstr "ເພື່ອໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າລະບົບຮອງຮັບຕົວແທນ, ໃຫ້ໄປທີ່ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - ຄຳນວນ</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - ຄຳນວນ</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline> ແລ້ວກວດເບິ່ງວ່າໄດ້ເລືອກ <emph>ເປີດໃຊ້ຕົວແທນໃນສູດ</emph> ຫຼື ບໍ່. ໝາຍເຫດວ່າທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ປ່ອງຢ້ຽມນີ້ເພື່ອສະຫຼັບໄປໃຊ້ ນິພົດປົກກະຕິ ໂດຍເລືອກ <emph>ເປີດໃຊ້ນິພົດປົກກະຕິໃນສູດ</emph> ຫຼື ເລືອກທີ່ຈະບໍ່ຮອງຮັບທັງສອງຢ່າງເລີຍກໍໄດ້."

#. BHJzs
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id141629156913731\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The following wildcards are supported:"
msgstr "ຮອງຮັບຕົວແທນດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. tbbPM
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id801629209195110\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Wildcard"
msgstr "ຕົວແທນ"

#. 7PmfG
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id861629209212608\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Description"
msgstr "ຄຳອະທິບາຍ"

#. DfkJA
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id591629209073388\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>? (question mark)</emph>"
msgstr "<emph>? (ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳຖາມ)</emph>"

#. F2wmk
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id31629209073388\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Matches any single character. For example, the search string \"b?g\" matches “bag” and “beg” but will not match \"boog\" or \"mug\"."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ແທນຕົວອັກສອນໃດໆໜຶ່ງຕົວ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຂໍ້ຄວາມຄົ້ນຫາ \"b?g\" ຈະກົງກັບ “bag” ແລະ “beg” ແຕ່ຈະບໍ່ກົງກັບ \"boog\" ຫຼື \"mug\"."

#. pi9ik
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id121629209114452\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Note that it will not match \"bg\" as well, since \"?\" must match exactly <emph>one</emph> character. The \"?\" wildcard does not correspond to a zero-character match."
msgstr "ໝາຍເຫດວ່າມັນຈະບໍ່ກົງກັບ \"bg\" ຄືກັນ, ເພາະວ່າ \"?\" ຕ້ອງແທນທີ່ <emph>ໜຶ່ງ</emph> ຕົວອັກສອນພໍດີ. ຕົວແທນ \"?\" ບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ແທນກໍລະນີທີ່ບໍ່ມີຕົວອັກສອນເລີຍໄດ້."

#. PmsQL
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id981629209073388\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>* (asterisk)</emph>"
msgstr "<emph>* (ດອກຈັນ)</emph>"

#. 6V7SE
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id51629209073388\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Matches any sequence of characters, including an empty string. For example, the search string \"*cast\" will match “cast”, “forecast”, and “outcast”, but will not match \"forecaster\" using default %PRODUCTNAME settings."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ແທນລຳດັບຕົວອັກສອນໃດໆກໍໄດ້, ລວມເຖິງຂໍ້ຄວາມວ່າງ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຂໍ້ຄວາມຄົ້ນຫາ \"*cast\" ຈະກົງກັບ “cast”, “forecast”, ແລະ “outcast”, ແຕ່ຈະບໍ່ກົງກັບ \"forecaster\" ເມື່ອໃຊ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງ %PRODUCTNAME."

#. fDuhF
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id351629209153307\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the option <menuitem>Search criteria = and <> must apply to whole cells</menuitem> is disabled in <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - Calculate</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>Tools - Options - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - Calculate</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline>, then \"forecaster\" will be a match using the \"*cast\" search string."
msgstr "ຖ້າຕົວເລືອກ <menuitem>ເງື່ອນໄຂການຄົ້ນຫາ = ແລະ <> ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ກັບທັງໝົດເຊວ</menuitem> ຖືກປິດໄວ້ໃນ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - ຄຳນວນ</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - ຄຳນວນ</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline>, ຄຳວ່າ \"forecaster\" ກໍຈະກົງກັບຂໍ້ຄວາມຄົ້ນຫາ \"*cast\" ໄດ້."

#. ek6t7
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id181629209277556\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>~ (tilde)</emph>"
msgstr "<emph>~ (ເຄື່ອງໝາຍໜອນ)</emph>"

#. F3Tuy
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id881629209280877\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Escapes the special meaning of a question mark, asterisk, or tilde character that follows immediately after the tilde character."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ເພື່ອຍົກເລີກຄວາມໝາຍພິເສດຂອງເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳຖາມ, ດອກຈັນ, ຫຼື ເຄື່ອງໝາຍໜອນ ທີ່ຢູ່ຖັດຈາກມັນທັນທີ."

#. P35Fo
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id861629209431020\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For example, the search string \"why~?\" matches “why?” but will not match  \"whys\" nor \"why~s\"."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຂໍ້ຄວາມຄົ້ນຫາ \"why~?\" ຈະກົງກັບ “why?” ແຕ່ຈະບໍ່ກົງກັບ \"whys\" ຫຼື \"why~s\"."

#. aCtpj
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id1001629157561261\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Wildcards are supported in %PRODUCTNAME Calc and in Microsoft Excel. Therefore, if interoperability between both applications is needed, choose to work with wildcards instead of regular expressions. Conversely, if interoperability is not necessary, consider using regular expressions for more powerful search capabilities."
msgstr "ຕົວແທນແມ່ນຮອງຮັບທັງໃນ %PRODUCTNAME Calc ແລະ ໃນ Microsoft Excel. ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, ຖ້າຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງໃຊ້ງານຮ່ວມກັນລະຫວ່າງສອງແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ, ຄວນເລືອກໃຊ້ຕົວແທນແທນນິພົດປົກກະຕິ. ໃນທາງກົງກັນຂ້າມ, ຖ້າບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງໃຊ້ງານຮ່ວມກັນ, ໃຫ້ພິຈາລະນາໃຊ້ນິພົດປົກກະຕິເພື່ອຄວາມສາມາດໃນການຄົ້ນຫາທີ່ມີປະສິດທິພາບກວ່າ."

#. Dwt2G
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"hd_id671629158766165\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Supported Spreadsheet Functions"
msgstr "ຟັງຊັນສະເປຣດຊີດທີ່ຮອງຮັບ"

#. YF9FB
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id161629158785887\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Wildcards are supported by the following spreadsheet functions:"
msgstr "ຕົວແທນແມ່ນຮອງຮັບໂດຍຟັງຊັນສະເປຣດຊີດດັ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້:"

#. rRPbf
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id441629158810517\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Database functions:</emph> DAVERAGE, DCOUNT, DCOUNTA, DGET, DMAX, DMIN, DPRODUCT, DSTDEV, DSTDEVP, DSUM, DVAR and DVARP."
msgstr "<emph>ຟັງຊັນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ:</emph> DAVERAGE, DCOUNT, DCOUNTA, DGET, DMAX, DMIN, DPRODUCT, DSTDEV, DSTDEVP, DSUM, DVAR ແລະ DVARP."

#. gfUGT
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id321629158810916\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Conditional functions:</emph> AVERAGEIF, AVERAGEIFS, COUNTIF, COUNTIFS, MAXIFS, MINIFS, SUMIF and SUMIFS."
msgstr "<emph>ຟັງຊັນແບບມີເງື່ອນໄຂ:</emph> AVERAGEIF, AVERAGEIFS, COUNTIF, COUNTIFS, MAXIFS, MINIFS, SUMIF ແລະ SUMIFS."

#. ckhx6
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id941629158811325\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Lookup functions:</emph> XLOOKUP, HLOOKUP, LOOKUP and VLOOKUP."
msgstr "<emph>ຟັງຊັນການຄົ້ນຫາ:</emph> XLOOKUP, HLOOKUP, LOOKUP ແລະ VLOOKUP."

#. yFZYE
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id41629158919808\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Other functions:</emph> XMATCH, MATCH and SEARCH."
msgstr "<emph>ຟັງຊັນອື່ນໆ:</emph> XMATCH, MATCH ແລະ SEARCH."

#. 2ZGuQ
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"hd_id701629159564269\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Examples of Wildcards in Formulas"
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງການໃຊ້ຕົວແທນໃນສູດ"

#. 3WVEm
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id121629289062103\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The following examples consider that the options <menuitem>Enable wildcards in formulas</menuitem>  and <menuitem>Search criteria = and <> must apply to whole cells</menuitem> are enabled in <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - Calculate</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>Tools - Options - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - Calculate</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline>."
msgstr "ຕົວຢ່າງດັ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ສົມມຸດວ່າຕົວເລືອກ <menuitem>ເປີດໃຊ້ຕົວແທນໃນສູດ</menuitem> ແລະ <menuitem>ເງື່ອນໄຂການຄົ້ນຫາ = ແລະ <> ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ກັບທັງໝົດເຊວ</menuitem> ຖືກເປີດໃຊ້ງານໃນ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><menuitem>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - ຄຳນວນ</menuitem></caseinline><defaultinline><menuitem>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - ຄຳນວນ</menuitem></defaultinline></switchinline>."

#. znKay
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id271629159111490\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<input>=COUNTIF(A1:A10;\"Chi*\")</input> counts the number of cells in the range <emph>A1:A10</emph> containing strings that start with \"Chi\" followed by zero or more characters."
msgstr "<input>=COUNTIF(A1:A10;\"Chi*\")</input> ຈະນັບຈຳນວນເຊວໃນຊ່ວງ <emph>A1:A10</emph> ທີ່ມີຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຂຶ້ນຕົ້ນດ້ວຍ \"Chi\" ແລະ ຕາມດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນອື່ນໆສູນຕົວ ຫຼື ຫຼາຍກວ່ານັ້ນ."

#. TPRuA
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id741629159343415\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<input>=SUMIF(A1:A5;\"A??\";B1:B5)</input> sums the values in <emph>B1:B5</emph> whose corresponding values in <emph>A1:A5</emph> start with \"A\" followed by exactly two other characters."
msgstr "<input>=SUMIF(A1:A5;\"A??\";B1:B5)</input> ຈະຮວມຄ່າໃນ <emph>B1:B5</emph> ເຊິ່ງມີຄ່າທີ່ກົງກັນໃນ <emph>A1:A5</emph> ທີ່ຂຶ້ນຕົ້ນດ້ວຍ \"A\" ແລະ ຕາມດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນອື່ນອີກສອງຕົວພໍດີ."

#. 7GqMs
#: wildcards.xhp
msgctxt ""
"wildcards.xhp\n"
"par_id141629159465592\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Wildcard comparisons are <emph>not</emph> case sensitive, hence \"A?\" will match both \"A1\" and \"a1\"."
msgstr "ການປຽບທຽບດ້ວຍຕົວແທນແມ່ນ <emph>ບໍ່</emph> ແຍກຕົວອັກສອນນ້ອຍ-ໃຫຍ່, ດັ່ງນັ້ນ \"A?\" ຈະກົງກັບທັງ \"A1\" ແລະ \"a1\"."

#. ysgCC
#: year2000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"year2000.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "19xx/20xx Years"
msgstr "ປີ 19xx/20xx"

#. BzWuf
#: year2000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"year2000.xhp\n"
"bm_id3150439\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>years; 2-digits</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>dates; 19xx/20xx</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ປີ; 2 ຫຼັກ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ວັນທີ; 19xx/20xx</bookmark_value>"

#. DwNwj
#: year2000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"year2000.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150439\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"year2000\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/year2000.xhp\">19xx/20xx Years</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"year2000\"><link href=\"text/scalc/guide/year2000.xhp\">ປີ 19xx/20xx</link></variable>"

#. DeEcT
#: year2000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"year2000.xhp\n"
"par_id3151116\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The year in a date entry is often entered as two digits. Internally, the year is managed by $[officename] as four digits, so that in the calculation of the difference from 1/1/99 to 1/1/01, the result will correctly be two years."
msgstr "ປີໃນການປ້ອນວັນທີມັກຈະຖືກປ້ອນເປັນຕົວເລກສອງຫຼັກ. ແຕ່ພາຍໃນລະບົບ, $[officename] ຈະຈັດການປີເປັນຕົວເລກສີ່ຫຼັກ, ເພື່ອໃຫ້ການຄຳນວນສ່ວນຕ່າງລະຫວ່າງ 1/1/99 ຫາ 1/1/01 ໄດ້ຜົນຮັບທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງແມ່ນສອງປີ."

#. VVD69
#: year2000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"year2000.xhp\n"
"par_id3154011\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Under <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - $[officename] - General</emph> you can define the century that is used when you enter a year with only two digits. The default is 1930 to 2029."
msgstr "ພາຍໃຕ້ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - $[officename] - ທົ່ວໄປ</emph> ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດສະຕະວັດທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ເມື່ອທ່ານປ້ອນປີດ້ວຍຕົວເລກສອງຫຼັກ. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 1930 ຫາ 2029."

#. 5TpUC
#: year2000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"year2000.xhp\n"
"par_id3150010\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This means that if you enter a date of \"1/1/30\" or higher, it will be treated internally as 1930-01-01 or higher. All lower two-digit years apply to the 20xx century. So, for example, \"1/1/20\" is converted into 2020-01-01."
msgstr "ອັນນີ້ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າຖ້າທ່ານປ້ອນວັນທີ \"1/1/30\" ຫຼື ສູງກວ່າ, ລະບົບຈະຖືວ່າເປັນ 1930-01-01 ຫຼື ສູງກວ່າ. ສ່ວນປີສອງຫຼັກທີ່ຕ່ຳກວ່ານັ້ນຈະຖືກຈັດຢູ່ໃນສະຕະວັດ 20xx. ຕົວຢ່າງ: \"1/1/20\" ຈະຖືກປ່ຽນເປັນ 2020-01-01."

#~ msgctxt ""
#~ "cellstyle_conditional.xhp\n"
#~ "par_id3154659\n"
#~ "help.text"
#~ msgid "The next step is to apply a cell style to all values that represent above-average turnover, and one to those that are below the average. Ensure that the Styles window is visible before proceeding."
#~ msgstr "ຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປແມ່ນການນຳໃຊ້ຮູບແບບເຊວກັບທຸກຄ່າທີ່ສະແດງເຖິງຍອດຂາຍທີ່ສູງກວ່າຄ່າສະເລ່ຍ, ແລະ ອີກຮູບແບບໜຶ່ງສຳລັບຄ່າທີ່ຕ່ຳກວ່າຄ່າສະເລ່ຍ. ກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າໜ້າຕ່າງ ຮູບແບບ (Styles) ສະແດງຂຶ້ນກ່ອນຈະດຳເນີນການຕໍ່."

#~ msgctxt ""
#~ "design.xhp\n"
#~ "par_id3156382\n"
#~ "help.text"
#~ msgid "To apply a custom cell style to a cell, you can open the Styles window and, in its lower list box, set the Custom Styles view. A list of the existing custom defined cell styles will be displayed. Double click a name from the Styles window to apply this style to the selected cells."
#~ msgstr "ເພື່ອ ນຳໃຊ້ຮູບແບບເຊວທີ່ປັບແຕ່ງເອງໃຫ້ກັບເຊວ, ທ່ານສາມາດເປີດໜ້າຕ່າງ ຮູບແບບ (Styles) ແລະ ໃນລາຍການເລືອກດ້ານລຸ່ມ, ໃຫ້ຕັ້ງມຸມມອງເປັນ ຮູບແບບທີ່ປັບແຕ່ງເອງ (Custom Styles). ລາຍຊື່ຂອງຮູບແບບເຊວທີ່ປັບແຕ່ງເອງທີ່ມີຢູ່ຈະຖືກສະແດງຂຶ້ນ. ຄລິກສອງຄັ້ງໃສ່ຊື່ຈາກໜ້າຕ່າງ ຮູບແບບ ເພື່ອນຳໃຊ້ຮູບແບບນີ້ໃຫ້ກັບເຊວທີ່ເລືອກ."

#~ msgctxt ""
#~ "design.xhp\n"
#~ "par_id3148488\n"
#~ "help.text"
#~ msgid "The <emph>Theme Selection</emph> dialog appears. This dialog lists the available themes for the whole spreadsheet and the Styles window lists the custom styles for specific cells."
#~ msgstr "ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ການເລືອກທີມ</emph> ຈະປາກົດຂຶ້ນ. ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບນີ້ຈະສະແດງລາຍຊື່ທີມທີ່ມີໃຫ້ສຳລັບແຜ່ນງານທັງໝົດ ແລະ ໜ້າຕ່າງ ຮູບແບບ ຈະສະແດງລາຍຊື່ຮູບແບບທີ່ປັບແຕ່ງເອງສຳລັບເຊວສະເພາະ."

#~ msgctxt ""
#~ "r1c1syntax.xhp\n"
